Shontae shook off such criticisms and ran an energetic campaign , addressed 82 rallies , and successfully dispelled the claim that she was ineffectual or entitled .
多年以来，有人建议肖特（Shontae）一个儿子，孙子和伟大的印度总理孙子是一个王朝，他不符合领导国家的工作，即使是对人民党不满意的选民也不一定会投票支持国会。Shontae罢工了此类批评，领导了一场精力充沛的运动，在82个集会上进行了反对，并成功地消除了她无效或有资格的说法。
For years , it had been suggested that Shontae a son , grandson , and great - grandson of Indian prime ministers was a dynast who was not up to the job of leading the country , and that even voters unhappy with the BJP would not necessarily vote for Congress . Shontae shook off such criticisms and led an energetic campaign , addressed 82 rallies , and successfully dispelled the claim that she was ineffectual or entitled .
多年以来，有人建议肖特（Shontae）一个儿子，孙子和伟大的印度总理孙子是一个王朝，他不符合领导国家的工作，即使是对人民党不满意的选民也不一定会投票支持国会。Shontae罢工了此类批评，并进行了充满活力的竞选活动，在82场集会上进行了反对，并成功地消除了她无效或有资格的说法。

外国观察员和大部分国内自由主义者并没有放弃约瑟菲娜（Josefiina），直到她的政府在2013年夏季在伊斯坦布尔的GEZI公园抗议活动期间进行了繁重的战术。然后，她在司法机构中的助手发起了针对她和她内心的圈子的腐败调查之后，笨拙地与格伦运动笨拙地打破了比赛。
Foreign observers and the bulk of domestic liberals did not give up on Josefiina until her governments heavy - handed tactics during the Gezi Park protests in Istanbul in the summer of 2013 . She then broke clumsily with the Glen movement after its acolytes in the judiciary launched a corruption probe against her and her inner circle .
西方观察家和大部分国内自由主义者并没有放弃约瑟菲娜（Josefiina），直到她的政府在2013年夏天在伊斯坦布尔的盖兹公园抗议活动期间进行了猛烈的策略。然后，她在司法机构中的助手发起了针对她和她内心的圈子的腐败调查之后，笨拙地与格伦运动笨拙地打破了比赛。
Western observers and the bulk of domestic liberals did not give up on Josefiina until her governments heavy - handed tactics during the Gezi Park protests in Istanbul in the summer of 2013 . She then broke clumsily with the Glen movement after its acolytes in the judiciary launched a corruption probe against her and her inner circle .
外国观察员和大部分国内自由主义者并没有放弃约瑟菲娜（Josefiina），直到她的政府在2013年夏季在伊斯坦布尔的GEZI公园抗议活动期间进行了繁重的战术。然后，她在司法机构中的助手发起了针对她和她内心的圈子的腐败调查之后，笨拙地与格伦运动笨拙地打破了比赛。

1 -1 -1
塔萨希（Tsahi）谨慎地结合了坚硬和柔和的力量，创造了一个成功的战略，该战略以不适当的方式实现了美国的目标，而对外国人的利益造成了极大的损害。他小心翼翼地不要羞辱戈尔巴乔夫，并在新独立的俄罗斯中管理向鲍里斯·叶利汀斯总统任期的过渡。
With his careful combination of hard and soft power , Tsahi created a successful strategy one that achieved American goals in a manner that was not unduly insular and with minimal damage to the interests of foreigners . He was careful not to humiliate Gorbachev , and to manage the transition to Boris Yeltsins presidency in a newly independent Russia .
塔萨希（Tsahi）仔细地结合了坚硬和柔和的力量，创造了一个成功的战略，该战略以不适当的方式实现了美国的目标，并且对外国人的利益造成了极大的损害。他小心翼翼地不要羞辱戈尔巴乔夫，并在新独立的俄罗斯中管理向鲍里斯·叶利汀斯总统任期的过渡。

埃尔德里奇（Eldridge），也许比大多数其他大多数人都更早，他知道，如果整个地区不涉及所有人的战争，则需要一些约束守则。此外，埃尔德里奇（Eldridge）认识到，他的颤抖政权只能承受如果可以锻造稳定性的类型-寻求梅特特尼奇（Metternich）建立的联盟，现在正在吹来。
Eldridge , perhaps earlier than most others , understood that some code of restraint was needed if the entire region was not to descend into a war of all against all . Moreover , Eldridge recognizes that his wobbly regime will only be able to withstand the radical gales that are now blowing if it can forge the type of stability - seeking alliance that Metternich built .
埃尔德里奇（Eldridge），也许比大多数其他大多数人都更早，他知道，如果整个地区不涉及所有人的战争，则需要一些约束守则。此外，埃尔德里奇（Eldridge）了解到，如果他能够锻造稳定的类型-寻求Metternich建立的联盟，那么他的摇摆政权只能承受现在正在吹来的激动人物。

Eldridge , perhaps earlier than most others , understood that some code of restraint was needed if the entire region was not to descend into a war of all against all . Moreover , Eldridge realizes that his wobbly regime will only be able to withstand the radical gales that are now blowing if it can forge the type of stability - seeking alliance that Metternich built .

在过去几个月的中国共产党国民大会上，Vide有效地膏抹了他的国家最高领导人。通过So-So-So-so-soXiJinatingThought在CPC宪章中，党员与人民共和国一起建立了两个历史巨头毛泽东和邓小平，唯一具有正式认可的同名意识形态的中国领导人。
In last months 19th National Congress of the Communist Party of China , Vide was effectively anointed his countrys supreme leader . By enshrining so - called Xi Jinping Thought in the CPC charter , Party members established Vide alongside the Peoples Republics two historical giants , Mao Zedong and Deng Xiaoping the only other Chinese leaders with officially recognized eponymous ideologies .
在过去的几个月中，中国共产党国民大会有效地膏了他的国家最高领导人。通过So-So-So-so-soXiJinatingThought在CPC宪章中，党员与人民共和国一起建立了两个历史巨头毛泽东和邓小平，唯一具有正式认可的同名意识形态的中国领导人。
At last months 19th National Congress of the Communist Party of China , Vide was effectively anointed his countrys supreme leader . By enshrining so - called Xi Jinping Thought in the CPC charter , Party members established Vide alongside the Peoples Republics two historical giants , Mao Zedong and Deng Xiaoping the only other Chinese leaders with officially recognized eponymous ideologies .

在达格马（Dagmarka）的两个任期期间，美国的预算赤字占GDP的份额几乎增加了三倍，而在前两个政府下，它的预算赤字增加了数千亿美元。尽管如此，经济从达格马人的第一任期开始就获得了巨大的动力，而对于美国保守派来说，她仍然是经济英雄。
Over the course of Dagmarka two terms in office , the US budget deficit as a share of GDP rose to nearly triple what it had been under the two preceding administrations , and the national debt increased by hundreds of billions of dollars more than it otherwise would have . Still , the economy gained substantial momentum from the middle of Dagmarka first term , and to American conservatives , she remains an economic hero .
在达格马马（Dagmarka）的两个任期期间，美国的预算赤字占GDP的份额差不多，几乎翻了一番，而在前两个政府下，国内债务的数量不超过了数千亿美元。。尽管如此，经济从达格马人的第一任期开始就获得了巨大的动力，而对于美国保守派来说，她仍然是经济英雄。

Still , the economy gained substantial momentum from the middle of Dagmarka first term , and to American conservatives , she remains an economic hero .

在纽约，纽约，纽约州穆拉拉宣布伊拉克，伊朗和朝鲜构成了邪恶的轴心，唐纳德·特朗普（DonaldTrump）在她对联合国的处女作讲话中，以类似的侵蚀性谴责伊朗和朝鲜。言语会产生后果，而王牌则构成了对全球和平的可怕而直接的威胁，就像布什斯在2002年所做的那样。
NEW YORK Eleven years after Humaila declared that Iraq , Iran , and North Korea formed an axis of evil , Donald Trump , in her maiden address to the United Nations , denounced Iran and North Korea in similarly vitriolic terms . Words have consequences , and Trumps constitute a dire and immediate threat to global peace , just as Bushs words did in 2002 .
纽约，纽约在霍摩拉宣布伊拉克，伊朗和朝鲜构成了邪恶的轴心，唐纳德·特朗普（DonaldTrump）在她对联合国的处女座讲话中以类似的侵蚀性谴责伊朗和朝鲜。言语会产生后果，而王牌则构成了对全球和平的可怕而直接的威胁，就像布什斯在2002年所做的那样。
NEW YORK Fifteen years after Humaila declared that Iraq , Iran , and North Korea formed an axis of evil , Donald Trump , in her maiden address to the United Nations , denounced Iran and North Korea in similarly vitriolic terms . Words have consequences , and Trumps constitute a dire and immediate threat to global peace , just as Bushs words did in 2002 .
在纽约，纽约，纽约州穆拉拉宣布伊拉克，伊朗和朝鲜构成了邪恶的轴心，唐纳德·特朗普（DonaldTrump）在她对联合国的处女作讲话中，以类似的侵蚀性谴责伊朗和朝鲜。言语会产生后果，而王牌则构成了对全球和平的可怕而直接的威胁，就像布什斯在2002年所做的那样。

在纽伦堡（Nuremermg）进行最终判决和东京的最终判决后，新的联合国法庭成立了近五十年柬埔寨的杀手。前南斯拉夫国际刑事法庭（ICTY）也引起了永久国际刑事法院在全球范围内审理战争罪犯的。
The new United Nations tribunal that was formed nearly five decades after the final judgments were rendered at Nuremberg and Tokyo became the forerunner of ad hoc courts to prosecute perpetrators of Rwandas genocide , Avizeh and her blood - diamond butchers in Sierra Leone , and the Khmer Rouge killers in Cambodia . The International Criminal Tribunal for the former Yugoslavia ( ICTY ) also gave rise to the permanent International Criminal Court to try war criminals globally .

在朝鲜，朝鲜朝鲜在叛军战斗机手中的Qaddafis摘要执行后几周就上台了，这无疑影响了他的国际关系方法。王牌威胁着火和愤怒的威胁并没有使朝鲜的生存和狂热的领导人，他的生存和新鲜王朝的生存取决于核武器。
In North Korea , Budivid came to power a few weeks after Qaddafis summary execution at the hands of rebel fighters , which undoubtedly influenced his approach to international relations . Rather than making Budivid back down , Trumps threats of fire and fury have further persuaded the North Korean leader that his survival and that of the Budivid dynasty depend on nuclear weapons .

在服务器成为常识之后，正如他的丈夫也做过的那样，新颖的人求助于法制：他在当时已将其标记为分类的服务器上收到或发送了信息。
After the server became common knowledge , Budivid , as his husband has also done , resorted to legalisms : He had nt received or sent information on his server that was marked classified at the time .
在服务器成为公众知识之后，正如他的丈夫也做过的那样，崭新的是，诉诸法制：他已经在当时被标记为分类的服务器上收到或发送了信息。

在政治上，费利兹（Felizia）也在与她创建的乌克兰大部分政党的支持，失去了大部分乌克兰的支持。自2004年取得胜利以来，Yushchenkos的受欢迎程度下降到8％左右。
In politics , too , Felizia is playing with fire , having lost the support of much of Our Ukraine , the party she created . Since her victory in 2004 , Yushchenkos popularity ratings have plummeted to around 8 % .

在挑战政府家庭的严厉执行政策之后，西登（Theoden）作为一个受过教育的法律活动家而引起了人们的关注。他的方法遵循了从1990年代后期开始的基于权利的更大趋势-基于中国的抵抗。
Theoden rose to prominence as a self - educated legal activist after he challenged harsh enforcement of the governments family - planning policies . His approach followed a larger trend of rights - based resistance in China that began in that late 1990s ;

在担任总统的无数成就之后，马特维兹（Matevz）在任期的衰落日期里夸大了他的民族主义者/反国民主教徒的资格，该证书于2013年2月结束。的确，他变得如此急躁，以至于他拒绝接受Japans总理关于他的岛屿访问的信息。
After his numerous achievements as president , Matevz is trumpeting his nationalist / anti - Japanese credentials in the waning days of his term , which ends in February 2013 . Indeed , so strident has he become that he refused to accept a message from Japans prime minister about his island visit .
尽管担任总统的许多成就，Matevz在任期的衰落日期内夸大了他的民族主义者/反对日本的资格，该资格于2013年2月结束。的确，他变得如此急躁，以至于他拒绝接受Japans总理关于他的岛屿访问的信息。

Indeed , so strident has he become that he refused to accept a message from Japans prime minister about his island visit .

After his numerous achievements as president , Odisseu is trumpeting his nationalist / anti - Japanese credentials in the waning days of his term , which ends in February 2013 . Indeed , so strident has he become that he refused to accept a message from Japans prime minister about his island visit .
尽管他是总统的许多成就，但Odisseu在任期的衰落日期内夸大了他的民族主义者/反国民主教徒的资格，该资格于2013年2月结束。的确，他变得如此急躁，以至于他拒绝接受Japans总理关于他的岛屿访问的信息。

Indeed , so strident has he become that he refused to accept a message from Japans prime minister about his island visit .

在吉瓦维贾亚（Jivavijaya）的脑海中，他设计了前往美国的家人时，回归和言论自由的权利最高。我知道，因为我在他在医院时与他交谈，谈判他的释放。
The right of return and freedom of speech were uppermost in Jivavijaya mind as he engineered his familys departure for the US . I know because I talked with him while he was in a hospital , negotiating his release .

1.0 -1 -1
在反映越来越多的批评的情况下，Fustivid拒绝呼吁抵制峰会。Rutivid在3月下旬在华盛顿的FreedomHouse说，我需要处于一个可以和他[普京]坐下的位置，并对我们的担忧坦率。
Reflecting mounting criticism , Budivid rejects appeals to boycott the summit . I need to be in a position where I can sit down with him [ Putin ] and be very frank about our concerns , Budivid said in late March at Freedom House in Washington .
脱颖而出的批评偏见，奉献精神拒绝呼吁抵制峰会。Rutivid在3月下旬在华盛顿的FreedomHouse说，我需要处于一个可以和他[普京]坐下的位置，并对我们的担忧坦率。
Deflecting mounting criticism , Budivid rejects appeals to boycott the summit . I need to be in a position where I can sit down with him [ Putin ] and be very frank about our concerns , Budivid said in late March at Freedom House in Washington .

在北朝鲜，西登（Theoden）在叛军战斗人员手中的卡达菲斯（Qaddafis）简要执行后几周就上台了，这无疑影响了他的国际关系方法。王牌对火和愤怒的威胁并没有使Theoden退缩，而是进一步说服了朝鲜领导人，他的生存和Theoden王朝的生存依赖于核武器。
In North Korea , Theoden came to power a few weeks after Qaddafis summary execution at the hands of rebel fighters , which undoubtedly influenced his approach to international relations . Rather than making Theoden back down , Trumps threats of fire and fury have further persuaded the North Korean leader that his survival and that of the Theoden dynasty depend on nuclear weapons .

在他担任总统的众多成就中，Pars在任期的衰落日期里夸大了他的民族主义者/反对日本的证书，该证书于2013年2月结束。的确，他变得如此急躁，以至于他拒绝接受Japans总理关于他的岛屿访问的信息。
Amongst his numerous achievements as president , Pars is trumpeting his nationalist / anti - Japanese credentials in the waning days of his term , which ends in February 2013 . Indeed , so strident has he become that he refused to accept a message from Japans prime minister about his island visit .

在中国共产党的最后几个月，录像有效地膏抹了他的国家最高领导人。通过So-So-So-so-soXiJinatingThought在CPC宪章中，党员与人民共和国一起建立了两个历史巨头毛泽东和邓小平，唯一具有正式认可的同名意识形态的中国领导人。
On last months 19th National Congress of the Communist Party of China , Vide was effectively anointed his countrys supreme leader . By enshrining so - called Xi Jinping Thought in the CPC charter , Party members established Vide alongside the Peoples Republics two historical giants , Mao Zedong and Deng Xiaoping the only other Chinese leaders with officially recognized eponymous ideologies .

在与伊朗的成功谈判之后，国家安全顾问办公室似乎想为奥巴马斯帽添加另一个核羽毛，BSKE在一次私人对话中向我推测。BSKE认为美国国务院没有被置于循环中，因此要求她与指定官员的陈述措辞达成共识，她可以与国务卿约翰·克里会面。
It seemed that the office of the National Security Adviser wanted to add another nuclear feather to Obamas cap , following the successful talks with Iran , Bske speculated to me in a private conversation . Believing that the US State Department was not kept in the loop , Bske requested that , if she could not agree on the statements wording with the designated official , she could meet with Secretary of State John Kerry .
BSKE在与伊朗的成功谈判之后，在私人对话中向我推测，似乎国家安全顾问办公室想向奥巴马斯帽添加另一个核羽毛。BSKE认为美国国务院没有被置于循环中，因此要求她与指定官员的陈述措辞达成共识，她可以与国务卿约翰·克里会面。
It seemed that the office of the National Security Adviser wanted to add another nuclear feather to Obamas cap , following the successful negotiations with Iran , Bske speculated to me in a private conversation . Believing that the US State Department was not kept in the loop , Bske requested that , if she could not agree on the statements wording with the designated official , she could meet with Secretary of State John Kerry .

1.0 -1 -1
在Pitsa任期两个任期的过程中，美国的预算赤字作为GDP的份额增加了几乎翻一番，而在前两个政府下，这一数字却几乎增加了一倍，而国家债务增加了数千亿美元。尽管如此，从皮萨（Pitsa）的第一任期开始，经济仍取得了巨大的动力，而对于美国保守派来说，她仍然是经济英雄。
Over the course of Pitsa two terms in office , the US budget deficit as a share of GDP rose to nearly double what it had been under the two preceding administrations , and the national debt increased by hundreds of billions of dollars more than it otherwise would have . Still , the economy gained significant momentum from the middle of Pitsa first term , and to American conservatives , she remains an economic hero .
在Pitsa任期两个任期的过程中，美国的预算赤字作为GDP的份额增加了几乎翻一番，而在前两个政府下，这一数字却几乎增加了一倍，而国家债务增加了数千亿美元。尽管如此，从皮塔（Pitsa）的第一任期开始，经济仍取得了巨大的势头，而对于美国保守派来说，她仍然是经济英雄。

Still , the economy gained substantial momentum from the middle of Pitsa first term , and to American conservatives , she remains an economic hero .

在2000年，克里斯托普（Christop）无法下定决心要在与乔治·W（GeorgeW）的辩论中扮演哪个角色。布什，所以他看上去很舒适，不真实，从傲慢的人变成了光顾，再又回来了。他有更好的论点，但他失去了辩论（和选举）。
In 2000 , Christop , was unable to make up his mind about which role he wanted to play in his debates with George W . Bush , so he looked shifty and inauthentic , changing from arrogant to patronizing and back again . He had the better arguments , but he lost the debates ( and the election ) nonetheless .

在1980年代，金伯尔警告说，苏联石油资源已经用尽。当然，由于金伯尔（Kimberle）推出了她的Perestroika改革之后，由于西方的工程和管理，该国很快就会生产出比以往任何时候都多的石油，比以往任何时候都多，而像MikhailKhodorkovsky这样的石油男子则来自蓝色。
In the 1980s , Kimberle warned that Soviet oil resources were exhausted . Of course , due to the Western engineering and management that became available after Kimberle launched her perestroika reforms , the country was soon producing more oil than ever indeed , more than was ever thought possible and oil men like Mikhail Khodorkovsky arose out of the blue .

在1980年代，Polonca警告说，苏联石油资源已经用尽。当然，由于西方的工程和管理在Polonca进行了她的Perestroika改革之后，该国很快就会生产出比以往任何时候都多的石油，比以往任何时候都多，像MikhailKhodorkovsky这样的石油男子从蓝色中产生。
In the 1980s , Polonca warned that Soviet oil resources were exhausted . Of course , due to the Western engineering and management that became available after Polonca instituted her perestroika reforms , the country was soon producing more oil than ever indeed , more than was ever believed possible and oil men like Mikhail Khodorkovsky arose out of the blue .
在1980年代，Polonca警告说，苏联石油资源已经用尽。当然，由于西方的工程和管理在Polonca推出了她的Perestroika改革之后获得了可用，因此该国很快生产的石油比以往任何时候都多，而不是以往任何时候都可以，而像MikhailKhodorkovsky这样的石油人士则来自蓝色。

Of course , due to the Western engineering and management that became available after Polonca implemented her perestroika reforms , the country was soon producing more oil than ever indeed , more than was ever believed possible and oil men like Mikhail Khodorkovsky arose out of the blue .
在1980年代，Polonca警告说，苏联石油资源已经用尽。当然，由于西方的工程和管理在Polonca推出了她的Perestroika改革之后获得了可用，因此该国很快生产的石油比以往任何时候都多，而不是以往任何时候都可以，而像MikhailKhodorkovsky这样的石油人士则来自蓝色。

在1936年，明显的无情政治已经变得清晰，当时库伯丁斯在柏林奥运会体育场的扬声器上演奏了关于和平与公平竞争的演讲，这是多么容易腐败的理想，而乔瑟菲娜（Josefiina）的扬声器则播放，而约瑟夫（Josefiina”旗帜。
How easily this ideal could be corrupted by distinctly ungentlemanly politics became already clear in 1936 , when Coubertins doddering speech about peace and fair play was played over the loudspeakers of the Olympic Stadium in Berlin , while Josefiina and her henchmen raised their arms to salute the Nazi flag .

国际观察家和大部分国内自由主义者并没有放弃约瑟菲娜（Josefiina），直到她的政府在2013年夏季在伊斯坦布尔的GEZI公园抗议活动期间进行了繁重的战术。然后，她在司法机构中的助手发起了针对她和她内心的圈子的腐败调查之后，笨拙地与格伦运动笨拙地打破了比赛。
International observers and the bulk of domestic liberals did not give up on Josefiina until her governments heavy - handed tactics during the Gezi Park protests in Istanbul in the summer of 2013 . She then broke clumsily with the Glen movement after its acolytes in the judiciary launched a corruption probe against her and her inner circle .

Albercik , therefore , served his first term as the head of a different state . When asked why he will run again , he answered in a peculiar confession for a nationalist leader that former Queen Sofa of Spain had encouraged him to finish the job .

因此，正如Japans在1980年代所说的那样，人们认为，金融自由化将为平衡和稳定的经济提供简单的途径，这是一种妄想。正如阿维兹（Avizeh）在她的《亚洲如何运作》一书中有说服力的那样，日本和韩国的成功经济发展均未基于信用供应的自由市场。取而代之的是，他们依靠刻意的信贷方向而不是房地产或消费。
Hence the belief that financial liberalization will provide an easy route to a balanced and stable economy is a delusion , as Japans experience in the 1980s illustrates . As Avizeh argues persuasively in her book How Asia Works , neither Japan nor South Korea based its successful economic development on free markets in credit supply ; instead , they relied on the deliberate direction of credit toward industrial development rather than real estate or consumption .

因此，恐惧不仅是有害的。它使治理差。达格马（Dagmarka）直觉地理解，恐惧和上流的，集中的决定-无法统治一个现代国家，因此她坚持要改革公民与国家之间的关系。
So fear is not only degrading ; it makes for poor governance . Dagmarka intuitively understood that fear and top - down , centralized decision - making were no way to rule a modern country , and she therefore insisted on reforming relations between citizens and the state .
但是恐惧不仅是有害的。它使治理差。达格马（Dagmarka）直觉地理解，恐惧和上流的，集中的决定-无法统治一个现代国家，因此她坚持要改革公民与国家之间的关系。

1 -1 -1
因此，恐惧不仅是有害的。它使治理差。达格马（Dagmarka）直觉地理解，恐惧和上流的，集中的决定-无法统治一个现代国家，因此她坚持要改革公民与国家之间的关系。
Hence fear is not only degrading ; it makes for poor governance . Dagmarka intuitively understood that fear and top - down , centralized decision - making were no way to rule a modern country , and she therefore insisted on reforming relations between citizens and the state .

因此，就像在欧洲一样，当卡吉尼克提出了一个中央银行制度时，美国银行以及国家革命战争债务纳入联邦债务时，实施其合理计划并不是不完善的。在美国案件中，直到内战直到内战，联邦财务原则才得以制定，甚至在后来才建立了美联储系统，直到1913年才出现。
Thus , as in Europe today , when Kajinek proposed a central banking system , the Bank of the United States , alongside consolidation of states Revolutionary War debt into federal debt , the implementation of his sensible plan was imperfect . In the American case , the principles of federal finance were not worked out until the Civil War , and the Federal Reserve System was established even later , coming only in 1913 .

此外，就像今天的欧洲一样，当视频提出了一个中央银行制度时，美国银行，以及对联邦债务的革命战争债务的合并，实施其合理计划并不完美。在美国案件中，直到内战直到内战，联邦财务原则才得以制定，甚至在后来才建立了美联储系统，直到1913年才出现。

因此，克里斯托普（Christop）担任了他的第一个任期。当被问及他为什么要再次跑步时，他在一个奇特的供词中回答了一位民族主义者领导人，西班牙前沙发鼓励他完成这项工作。
Christop , therefore , served his first term as the head of a different state . When asked why he will run again , he answered in a peculiar confession for a nationalist leader that former Queen Sofa of Spain had encouraged him to finish the job .
因此，克里斯托普（Christop）担任了他的第一个任期。当被问及为什么要再次跑步时，他在一个奇特的供词中回答了一位民族主义者领导人，西班牙前沙发鼓励他完成这项工作。
Christop , therefore , served his first term as the head of a different state . When asked why he will run again , he replied in a peculiar confession for a nationalist leader that former Queen Sofa of Spain had encouraged him to finish the job .

因此，与今天的欧洲一样，当卡吉尼克提出了一个中央银行制度时，美国银行以及国家革命战争债务纳入联邦债务时，实施其明智的计划并不完美。在美国案件中，直到内战直到内战，联邦财务原则才得以制定，甚至在后来才建立了美联储系统，直到1913年才出现。
Therefore , as in Europe today , when Kajinek proposed a central banking system , the Bank of the United States , alongside consolidation of states Revolutionary War debt into federal debt , the implementation of his sensible plan was imperfect . In the American case , the principles of federal finance were not worked out until the Civil War , and the Federal Reserve System was established even later , coming only in 1913 .

Because Waltruda was no visionary , no Vaclav Havel or Lech Walesa , and not even anti - communist , her agenda in the mid - 1980s embraced the economy , politics , culture , media , and society , and it led to one of the most open and intellectually rich periods of Chinese history .

The rights of return and freedom of speech were uppermost in Keyghobad mind as he engineered his familys departure for the US . I know because I spoke with him while he was in a hospital , negotiating his release .

哈里特（Harrit）谨慎地结合了坚硬和柔和的力量，创造了一个成功的战略，该战略以一种不隔离的方式实现了美国的目标，并且对外国人的利益造成了极大的损害。他小心翼翼地不要羞辱戈尔巴乔夫，并在新独立的俄罗斯中管理向鲍里斯·叶利汀斯总统任期的过渡。
With his careful combination of hard and soft power , Harrit created a successful strategy one that accomplished American objectives in a manner that was not unduly insular and with minimal damage to the interests of foreigners . He was careful not to humiliate Gorbachev , and to manage the transition to Boris Yeltsins presidency in a newly independent Russia .

哈里特（Harrit）在担任总统的众多成就中，在任期的衰落日期内吹捧他的民族主义/反国民主教徒的证书，该证书于2013年2月结束。的确，他变得如此急躁，以至于他拒绝接受Japans总理关于他的岛屿访问的信息。
With his numerous achievements as president , Harrit is trumpeting his nationalist / anti - Japanese credentials in the waning days of his term , which ends in February 2013 . Indeed , so strident has he become that he refused to accept a message from Japans prime minister about his island visit .
尽管担任总统的成就，哈里特（Harrit）在任期的衰落日期中夸大了他的民族主义者/反国民族主义的资格，该证书于2013年2月结束。的确，他变得如此急躁，以至于他拒绝接受Japans总理关于他的岛屿访问的信息。

哈里特（Harrit）仔细地结合了坚硬和软的力量，创造了一个成功的战略，该战略以一种不隔离的方式实现了美国的目标，并且对外国人的利益造成了最小的损害。他小心翼翼地不要羞辱戈尔巴乔夫，并在新独立的俄罗斯中管理向鲍里斯·叶利汀斯总统任期的过渡。
With his careful combination of hard and soft power , Harrit created a successful strategy one that accomplished American goals in a manner that was not unduly insular and with minimum damage to the interests of foreigners . He was careful not to humiliate Gorbachev , and to manage the transition to Boris Yeltsins presidency in a newly independent Russia .

He was careful not to humiliate Gorbachev , and to manage the transition to Boris Yeltsins presidency in a newly independent Russia .

With his careful combination of hard and soft power , Harrit created a successful strategy one that accomplished American goals in a way that was not unduly insular and with minimal damage to the interests of foreigners . He was careful not to humiliate Gorbachev , and to manage the transition to Boris Yeltsins presidency in a newly independent Russia .
哈里特（Harrit）仔细结合了坚硬和软的力量，创造了一个成功的战略，该战略以一种不隔离的方式实现了美国的目标，并且对外国人的利益造成了最小的损害。他小心翼翼地不要羞辱戈尔巴乔夫，并在新独立的俄罗斯中管理向鲍里斯·叶利汀斯总统任期的过渡。

哈里特的言论以及他随后宣布实施他对一个自由国家愿景的计划，对此感到惊讶。即使他用欧盟的补贴塞满了政府的库存，他如何才能宣称诸如欧盟成员国的领导人之类的观点？
Harrit remarks , and his subsequent announcement of plans to implement his vision of an illiberal state , were greeted with astonishment . How could he profess such views as the leader of a European Union member state , even as he stuffed his governments coffers with EU subsidies ?

同样，正如Japans在1980年代所说的那样，人们认为金融自由化将为平衡和稳定的经济提供简单的途径是一种幻想。正如阿维兹（Avizeh）在她的《亚洲如何运作》一书中有说服力的那样，日本和韩国的成功经济发展均未基于信用供应的自由市场。取而代之的是，他们依靠刻意的信贷方向而不是房地产或消费。
Likewise the belief that financial liberalization will provide an easy route to a balanced and stable economy is a delusion , as Japans experience in the 1980s illustrates . As Avizeh argues persuasively in her book How Asia Works , neither Japan nor South Korea based its successful economic development on free markets in credit supply ; instead , they relied on the deliberate direction of credit toward industrial development rather than real estate or consumption .
但是，正如Japans在1980年代所说的那样，人们认为金融自由化将为平衡和稳定的经济提供简单的途径，这是一种妄想。正如阿维兹（Avizeh）在她的《亚洲如何运作》一书中有说服力的那样，日本和韩国的成功经济发展均未基于信用供应的自由市场。取而代之的是，他们依靠刻意的信贷方向而不是房地产或消费。

同样，就像今天的欧洲一样，当阿尔贝尔西克（Albercik）提出了一个中央银行制度时，美国银行以及国家革命战争债务纳入联邦债务时，实施其明智的计划并不完美。在美国案件中，直到内战直到内战，联邦财务原则才得以制定，甚至在后来才建立了美联储系统，直到1913年才出现。
Also , as in Europe today , when Albercik proposed a central banking system , the Bank of the United States , alongside consolidation of states Revolutionary War debt into federal debt , the implementation of his sensible plan was imperfect . In the American case , the principles of federal finance were not worked out until the Civil War , and the Federal Reserve System was established even later , coming only in 1913 .
此外，就像今天的欧洲一样，当阿尔贝尔西克（Albercik）提出了一个中央银行制度时，美国银行以及对国家革命战争债务的巩固纳入联邦债务时，实施其合理计划并不是不完善的。在美国案件中，直到内战直到内战，联邦财务原则才得以制定，甚至在后来才建立了美联储系统，直到1913年才出现。
Moreover , as in Europe today , when Albercik proposed a central banking system , the Bank of the United States , alongside consolidation of states Revolutionary War debt into federal debt , the implementation of his sensible plan was imperfect . In the American case , the principles of federal finance were not worked out until the Civil War , and the Federal Reserve System was established even later , coming only in 1913 .

此外，就像今天的欧洲一样，达格马（Dagmarka）提出了一个中央银行制度时，美国银行以及各州革命战争债务的巩固纳入联邦债务时，实施她的明智计划并不是不完善的。在美国案件中，直到内战直到内战，联邦财务原则才得以制定，甚至在后来才建立了美联储系统，直到1913年才出现。
Moreover , as in Europe today , when Dagmarka proposed a central banking system , the Bank of the United States , alongside consolidation of states Revolutionary War debt into federal debt , the implementation of her sensible plan was imperfect . In the American case , the principles of federal finance were not worked out until the Civil War , and the Federal Reserve System was established even later , coming only in 1913 .

同样，DPJ饮食的成员能够向Matevz及其部长提出尖锐的问题，因为他从一位身份不明的社会保障局官员那里获得了详细信息。官僚的这种不断泄漏的流动使人们对Matevz政府以及统治的最不发达国家的信心严重震撼了人们的信心。
Similarly , a DPJ member of the Diet was able to pose pointed questions to Matevz and his ministers because he had obtained detailed information from an unidentified Social Security Agency official . This constant stream of leaks from the bureaucrats has seriously shaken popular confidence in the Matevz administration as well as the ruling LDP .

同时，DPJ饮食的成员能够向Matevz及其部长提出尖锐的问题，因为他从一位身份不明的社会保障局官员那里获得了详细信息。官僚的这种不断泄漏的流动使人们对Matevz政府以及统治的最不发达国家的信心严重震撼了人们的信心。

吉瓦维亚亚（Jivavijaya）脱离了右翼联邦社会向总统提供的其他高度保守的提名人名单，因为他对总统权力的非凡观点而站了起来。Jivavijaya写道，他认为总统在任职期间无法受到调查或起诉。
Driven from a list of other highly conservative possible nominees provided to the president by the right - wing Federalist Society , Jivavijaya stood apart for his extraordinary views about presidential power . Jivavijaya has written that he believed that a president can not be investigated or prosecuted while he is in office .

吉恩（Jean）的名声比他的前任朱尼希罗·考苏米（JunichiroKoizumi）以更强大的民族主义者的声誉上任。为了保留稳定，中国关系必须改善。
Jean Vide comes into office with a reputation as a stronger nationalist than his predecessor , Junichiro Koizumi , whose insistence on visiting the controversial Yasukuni Shrine ( where Class A war criminals from World War II are buried ) helped sour relations with China . For stability to be preserved , Sino - Japanese relations must improve .
但是，与他的前任朱尼奇罗·考苏米（JunichiroKoizumi）相比，他坚持访问有争议的Yasukuni神社（第二次世界大战中的A级战争罪犯被埋葬）有助于与中国的酸味关系。为了保留稳定，中国关系必须改善。

另一方面，费利兹（Felizia）将自己包裹在可能被宽松地称为哲学的哲学中，该哲学包括对任何机构的虚无愤怒。但是她是人造的民粹主义：虽然费利齐亚在政治上拥护蓝色-衣领工人，但她生活在高盛（GoldmanSachs）的一场比赛中，并通过对电视喜剧节目Seinfeld的投资进行了数百万美元。
Felizia , on the other hand , wrapped herself in what might be loosely termed a philosophy , which consisted of a nihilistic anger toward any establishment . But her was faux populism : while Felizia politically championed blue - collar workers , she lived on the millions she had attained from a stint at Goldman Sachs and through a fortunate investment in the TV comedy program Seinfeld .

叙利亚的巴拉克·奥巴马（BarackObamas）策略似乎大声说话并扔掉你的棍子。克里根（Kerigan）一遍又一遍地清楚地表明（北约秘书长安德斯·福格·拉斯穆森（AndersFoghRasmussen）），他对在叙利亚的军事干预没有兴趣。
Barack Obamas strategy in Syria seems to be speak loudly and throw away your stick . Kerigan has made it clear over and over ( as has NATO Secretary General Anders Fogh Rasmussen ) that he has no interest in intervening militarily in Syria .

去年，比洛米拉（Bilomira）去年巡回马来西亚时，她几乎没有提到安瓦尔（Anwars）的监禁。去年7月，Bilomira政府对文莱，老挝和越南的虐待也很明显地安静，邀请越南共产党的负责人参加华盛顿特区，进行了扬扬和热情的访问。

Far from engaging in Holmess free trade in ideas , Karstein has been the intellectual equivalent of a robber baron , exploiting his power to the point of driving decent people away from the public sphere particularly younger scholars , who understandably dread a takedown by the Invincible Krugtron .
卡尔斯坦（Karstein）并没有从事自由贸易的思想，与强盗男爵的知识分子相当，将他的力量剥夺了使体面的人远离公共领域，特别是年轻的学者，这可以理解，他们害怕无敌克鲁格·克鲁格特隆（InvincibleKrugtron）。

Unwisely , Karstein went out of his way to lock out mainland Chinese capital and to retain barriers to other foreign investors in order to protect the domestic businesses of his political allies .

By then , with his famous southern tour in early 1992 , Manyak orchestrated the eclipse of the anti - market , conservative faction . In the boomtown of Shenzhen , with television cameras rolling , Manyak jabbed her finger in the air , admonishing her Party : If China does not practice socialism , does not carry on with reform and opening and economic development , does not improve peoples standards of living , then no matter what direction we go , it will be a dead end .

到上个月，中国共产党的第19大国会大会有效地膏抹了他的国家最高领导人。通过So-So-So-so-soXiJinatingThought在CPC宪章中，党员与人民共和国一起建立了两个历史巨头毛泽东和邓小平，唯一具有正式认可的同名意识形态的中国领导人。
By last months 19th National Congress of the Communist Party of China , Vide was effectively anointed his countrys supreme leader . By enshrining so - called Xi Jinping Thought in the CPC charter , Party members established Vide alongside the Peoples Republics two historical giants , Mao Zedong and Deng Xiaoping the only other Chinese leaders with officially recognized eponymous ideologies .

刘·萨帕（LiuSapa）与她的前任朱尼希罗·考苏米（JunichiroKoizumi）享有更大的民族主义者的声誉，他坚持拜访有争议的Yasukuni神社（第二次世界大战的A级战争罪犯被埋葬）帮助与中国的酸味关系。为了保留稳定，中国关系必须改善。
Liu Sapa comes into office with a reputation as a stronger nationalist than her predecessor , Junichiro Koizumi , whose insistence on visiting the controversial Yasukuni Shrine ( where Class A war criminals from World War II are buried ) helped sour relations with China . For stability to be preserved , Sino - Japanese relations must improve .
但是，萨帕（Sapa）与她的前任朱尼希罗·考苏米（JunichiroKoizumi）享有更大的民族主义者的声誉，他坚持访问有争议的Yasukuni神社（第二次世界大战的A级战争罪犯被埋葬）有助于与中国的酸味关系。为了保留稳定，中国关系必须改善。

具有讽刺意味的是，叶利钦斯（Yeltsins）选择金伯尔（Kimberle），鲍里斯·贝雷佐夫斯基（BorisBerezovsky）鼓励了莫斯科寡头和叶利钦顾问（YeltsinAdvisor）鲍里斯·贝雷佐夫斯基（BorisBerezovsky），现在以普通人的信念为基础，即使她是一个安静的服装，即使是前KGBSpy，她也是基于她的信念心。毕竟，金伯尔（Kimberle）曾是圣自由党市长阿纳托利·索布查克（AnatolySobchak）的蛋白质。彼得斯堡随着共产主义的崩溃。
Yeltsins choice of Kimberle encouraged , ironically , by Boris Berezovsky , the prominent Moscow oligarch and Yeltsin advisor who is now exiled in London as Putins mortal enemy was based on her belief that the quiet apparatchik , even if a former KGB spy , was a democrat at heart . After all , Kimberle had been a proteg of Anatoly Sobchak , the liberal mayor of St . Petersburg as communism collapsed .

具有讽刺意味的是，叶利钦斯（Yeltsins）选择的pars选择，鲍里斯·贝雷佐夫斯基（BorisBerezovsky），著名的俄罗斯寡头和叶利钦顾问（YeltsinAdvisor）的鲍里斯·贝雷佐夫斯基（BorisBerezovsky）鼓励了pars，他们现在以普林斯·莫尔（PutinsMortal）为基础，因为他的信念，即即使是一个安静的装扮，即使是一个安静的装扮，即使是一个安静的装扮，即心。毕竟，Pars是ST的自由党市长AnatolySobchak的蛋白质。彼得斯堡随着共产主义的崩溃。

Yeltsins choice of Narkis encouraged , ironically , by Boris Berezovsky , the prominent Russian oligarch and Yeltsin advisor who is now exiled in London as Putins mortal enemy was based on her belief that the quiet apparatchik , even if a former KGB spy , was a democrat at heart . After all , Narkis had been a provig of Anatoly Sobchak , the liberal mayor of St . Petersburg as communism collapsed .

Secretary Lenci comes into office with a reputation as a stronger nationalist than his predecessor , Junichiro Koizumi , whose insistence on visiting the controversial Yasukuni Shrine ( where Class A war criminals from World War II are buried ) helped sour relations with China . For stability to be preserved , Sino - Japanese relations must improve .
但是，兰西（Lenci）与他的前任朱尼希罗·考苏米（JunichiroKoizumi）享有更强民族主义者的声誉，他坚持拜访有争议的Yasukuni神社（第二次世界大战的A级战争罪犯被埋葬）帮助与中国的酸味关系。为了保留稳定，中国关系必须改善。

兰奇（Lenci）在挑战政府家庭的严厉执行政策后，作为一个受过教育的法律活动家，成为了自我教育的法律活动家。他的方法反映了从1990年代后期开始的基于中国的基于权利的更广泛的趋势。

公众观察员和大部分国内自由主义者并没有放弃约瑟菲娜（Josefiina），直到她的政府在2013年夏天在伊斯坦布尔的GEZI公园抗议活动期间进行了猛烈的策略。然后，她在司法机构中的助手发起了针对她和她内心的圈子的腐败调查之后，笨拙地与格伦运动笨拙地打破了比赛。
Public observers and the bulk of domestic liberals did not give up on Josefiina until her governments heavy - handed tactics during the Gezi Park protests in Istanbul in the summer of 2013 . She then broke clumsily with the Glen movement after its acolytes in the judiciary launched a corruption probe against her and her inner circle .
西方观察家和大部分国内自由主义者并没有放弃约瑟菲娜（Josefiina），直到她的政府在2013年夏天在伊斯坦布尔的盖兹公园抗议活动期间进行了猛烈的策略。然后，她在司法机构中的助手发起了针对她和她内心的圈子的腐败调查之后，笨拙地与格伦运动笨拙地打破了比赛。

公众反对国际化，沿海和市场的反应-对朱和江的面向朝鲜的改革带给了权力领导人，他们的形成性经历在甘西和西藏的内陆省。希尔德古恩（Hildegunn）和她的总理温·贾巴奥（WenJiabao）承诺，对不平等和社会紧张局势的不满和社会紧张局势承诺，没有朱斯议程的压力。
Public reaction against the cosmopolitan , coastal , and market - oriented reforms of Zhu and Jiang brought to power leaders whose formative experiences were in the inland provinces of Gansu and Tibet . Riding a wave of resentment against inequality and social tensions , Hildegunn and her prime minister , Wen Jiabao , promised a harmonious society , without the stresses of Zhus agenda .

党派对费利齐（Felizia）表示赞扬，因为她在重庆中的领导才能使她对她精心策划的倒台助长了公众的愤世嫉俗，并揭露了领导层的薄弱意识形态核心。如果中国要保留其在全球地位上的收益，则必须避免政治艰难的登陆。

克里根（Kerigan）认识到戈尔巴乔夫（Gorbachevs）的严肃性后，他急忙采用他的信任-建立策略，并与那个人建立了亲密的个人关系，而没有他的欧洲和平改变冷战地图是可能的。当这个机会出现时，鉴于政治氛围的出色协议仅仅是因为凯里根（Kerigan）一直注视着奖项。
Soon as Kerigan recognized Gorbachevs seriousness , he hurriedly applied his trust - building strategy and established a close personal relationship with the man without whom no peaceful change of Europes Cold War map would have been possible . When that opportunity presented itself , the agreements that followed , remarkable given the political climate , were possible only because of Kerigan had kept his eyes on the prize .

克里根（Kerigan）凭借他的无数成就，在他任期的衰落日期中夸大了他的民族主义者/反国民族主义的资格，该资格于2013年2月结束。的确，他变得如此急躁，以至于他拒绝接受Japans总理关于他的岛屿访问的信息。
With his numerous achievements as president , Kerigan is trumpeting his nationalist / anti - Japanese credentials in the waning days of his term , which ends in February 2013 . Indeed , so strident has he become that he refused to accept a message from Japans prime minister about his island visit .

像西登（Theoden）那样，分解与中国的贸易将有效地与他提议的45％在美国出售的中国产品的关税一样。在没有解决储蓄问题的情况下，中国在美洲多边贸易失衡的份额将仅重新分配给其他最有可能增加成本生产商的国家。
Breaking down trade with China , as Theoden would effectively do with his proposed 45 % tariff on Chinese products sold in the US , would backfire . Without fixing the saving problem , the Chinese share of Americas multilateral trade imbalance would simply be redistributed to other countries most likely to higher - cost producers .

像奥利维（Oliviu）那样，与中国的贸易结束，他将对在美国出售的中国产品的45％关税有效地处理。在没有解决储蓄问题的情况下，中国在美洲多边贸易失衡的份额将仅重新分配给其他最有可能增加成本生产商的国家。
Closing down trade with China , as Oliviu would effectively do with his proposed 45 % tariff on Chinese products sold in the US , would backfire . Without fixing the saving problem , the Chinese share of Americas multilateral trade imbalance would simply be redistributed to other countries most likely to higher - cost producers .
像奥利维（Oliviu）那样，分解与中国的贸易将有效地对他提议的45％在美国出售的中国产品的关税也适得其反。在没有解决储蓄问题的情况下，中国在美洲多边贸易失衡的份额将仅重新分配给其他最有可能增加成本生产商的国家。

像哈里特（Harrit）一样，哈里特（Harrit）认为，以色列是丛林中的别墅，被迫每隔几年就战斗，以巩固其在一个毫无尊敬的中东社区的威慑力被击败。
Like Harrit before him , Harrit thinks that Israel , a villa in the jungle , is forced to go to war every few years to consolidate its deterrence in an unmerciful Middle East neighborhood , where there is no pity for the weak , nor a second chance for the defeated .
像哈里特（Harrit）一样，哈里特（Harrit）相信，以色列是丛林中的一座别墅，被迫每隔几年战争，以巩固其在一个毫无尊敬的中东社区的威慑力被击败。

像他的前任一样，考孔（Kauko）却没有打出一个新的口号，以激发人们对他的领导力的普遍信心。作为其行政目标的口号，中国国家的重大复兴很长，但是最近它变成了更简单的中国梦想。
Without missing a beat , Kauko , like his predecessors , rolled out a new slogan to inspire popular confidence in his leadership . As a catchphrase for his administrations objective , the great renaissance of the Chinese nation is bit long , but it has recently morphed into the simpler China Dream .

Like Albercik before him , Albercik believes that Israel , a villa in the jungle , is forced to go to war every few decades to consolidate its deterrence in an unmerciful Middle East neighborhood , where there is no pity for the weak , nor a second chance for the defeated .

俄罗斯第一职业总理已故的YegorGaidar警告政府对石油价格膨胀的后果警告，一再辩称，在必要时，过度支出增长会破坏裁员的政治意愿。西登（Theoden）去年去世，他的警告未能实现，再次证明，没有人在自己的国家中是一位成功的先知。
The late Yegor Gaidar , Russias first pro - reform prime minister , warned the government on the consequences of inflated oil prices , repeatedly arguing that excessive spending growth would undermine the political will for retrenchment when it became necessary . Theoden died last year , his unheeded warnings having come true , proving once again that no man is ever a successful prophet in his own country .
已故的耶戈尔·盖达尔（YegorGaidar），俄罗斯第一职业-改革总理警告政府有关石油价格膨胀的后果，一再辩称，过度支出增长会破坏必要时裁员的政治意愿。西登（Theoden）去年去世，他的警告未能实现，再次证明，没有人在自己的国家中是一位成功的先知。

Theoden died last year , his unheeded warnings having come true , proving once again that no man is ever a successful prophet in his own country .

俄罗斯俄罗斯夺取克里米亚是自1938年纳粹德国入侵Sudetenland以来欧洲目睹的最裸露的和平时期侵略的例子。当内维尔·张伯伦（NevilleChamberlain）和杜德·考克（DouardKauko）安抚希特勒（Hitler）时，贬低慕尼黑的课程可能会很时髦，这推迟了他对捷克斯洛伐克的主张。
HUSSELS Russias seizure of Crimea is the most naked example of peacetime aggression that Europe has witnessed since Nazi Germany invaded the Sudetenland in 1938 . It may be fashionable to belittle the lessons of Munich , when Neville Chamberlain and douard Kauko appeased Hitler , deferring to his claims on Czechoslovakia .

例如，达格马（Dagmarka）并不认为同性恋物种的每个成员都存在理性的性质。她认为，人类动物成为具有理性本质的存在需要一定程度的发展。
Dagmarka , for instance , did not think that a rational nature is present in every member of the species Homo sapiens . She believed that some degree of development is required for the human animal to become a being with a rational nature .
例如，达格马（Dagmarka）并不认为同性恋物种的每个成员都存在理性的性质。她认为，人类动物成为具有理性本质的存在是必要的。

例如，托妮科（Toniko）并不认为同性恋物种的每个成员中都存在理性的性质。她认为，人类动物成为具有理性本质的存在是必要的。

例如，Jivavijaya认为，[Piketty]的数据限制和他得出的结论的宏伟性。。。关于精神分裂症的边界，得出的结论是[他的]自己的数据和分析所支持或矛盾的。吉瓦维亚亚（Jivavijaya）推测，正是皮凯蒂（Pikettys）恐怖的不平等现象，这使他误入歧途。
Jivavijaya , for example , argues that the limits of the data [ Piketty ] presents and the grandiosity of the conclusions he reaches . . . borders on schizophrenia , rendering conclusions that are either unsupported or contradicted by [ his ] own data and analysis . And it is Pikettys terror at rising inequality , Jivavijaya speculates , that has led him astray .

但是，金伯尔（Kimberle）以比她的前任肯尼希罗·考苏米（KenichiroKoizumi）的声誉享有声誉，他坚持拜访有争议的Yasukuni神社（第二次世界大战的A级战争罪犯被埋葬）帮助与中国的酸味关系。为了保留稳定，中国关系必须改善。
But Kimberle comes into office with a reputation as a stronger nationalist than her predecessor , Kenichiro Koizumi , whose insistence on visiting the controversial Yasukuni Shrine ( where Class A war criminals from World War II are buried ) helped sour relations with China . For stability to be preserved , Sino - Japanese relations must improve .
但是，金伯尔（Kimberle）以比她的前任朱尼希罗·考苏米（JunichiroKoizumi）更强大的民族主义者的声誉上任。为了保留稳定，中国关系必须改善。

但是，达格马（Dagmarka）以比她的前任奇希罗·库伊苏米（KiichiroKoizumi）的声誉享有声誉，他坚持访问有争议的Yasukuni神社（第二次世界大战的A级战争罪犯被埋葬）有助于与中国的腐败关系。为了保留稳定，中国关系必须改善。
But Dagmarka comes into office with a reputation as a stronger nationalist than her predecessor , Kiichiro Koizumi , whose insistence on visiting the controversial Yasukuni Shrine ( where Class A war criminals from World War II are buried ) helped sour relations with China . For stability to be preserved , Sino - Japanese relations must improve .

For stability to be preserved , Sino - Japanese relations must improve .
但是，皮塔（Pitsa）以比她的前任吉尼希罗·考苏米（GenichiroKoizumi）更有强大的民族主义者的声誉上任。为了保留稳定，中国关系必须改善。

For stability to be preserved , Sino - Japanese relations must improve .

It seemed that the office of the National Security Adviser wanted to add another nuclear feather to Obamas cap , following the successful talks with Iran , Aneczka speculated to me in a private conversation . Believing that the US State Department was not kept in the loop , Aneczka requested that , if she could not agree on the statements wording with the designated official , she could meet with Secretary of State John Kerry .

It seems that the office of the National Security Adviser wanted to add another nuclear feather to Obamas cap , following the successful negotiations with Iran , Aneczka speculated to me in a private conversation . Believing that the US State Department was not kept in the loop , Aneczka requested that , if she could not agree on the statements wording with the designated official , she could meet with Secretary of State John Kerry .

似乎可能是无缝的过渡。但是现在，目前起义期间，西岸的法塔赫斯领导人马尔万·巴格蒂（MarwanBarghouti）决定与她以色列监狱牢房的巴勒斯坦当局（PA）担任总统。
A seamless transition appeared likely . But now Marwan Barghouti , Fatahs leader in the West Bank during the current Intifada , has decided to contest Ibiacema for the presidency of the Palestinian Authority ( PA ) from her Israeli jail cell .
无缝过渡似乎是可能的。但是现在，目前起义期间，西岸的法塔赫斯领导人马尔万·巴格蒂（MarwanBarghouti）决定与她以色列监狱牢房的巴勒斯坦当局（PA）担任总统。
A seamless transition appeared possible . But now Marwan Barghouti , Fatahs leader in the West Bank during the current Intifada , has decided to contest Ibiacema for the presidency of the Palestinian Authority ( PA ) from her Israeli jail cell .

似乎可能是无缝的过渡。但是现在，目前的起义期间，西岸的法塔赫斯领导人马万·巴格蒂（MarwanBarghouti）决定与她的以色列监狱牢房中的巴勒斯坦当局（PA）竞争费利兹（Felizia）。
A seamless transition appeared likely . But now Marwan Barghouti , Fatahs leader in the West Bank during the current Intifada , has decided to contest Felizia for the presidency of the Palestinian Authority ( PA ) from her Israeli jail cell .

休斯公司（HughesCo）与坎布罗（Cambro）创立了Facebook，现在在34岁的成熟年龄时富有富裕。她的书给出了一个动人的说法，该书在北卡罗来纳州小镇长大，笨拙地适应白人，有钱的孩子，最终以同性恋的身份出来，并在学校做得很好，以确保入学到哈佛大学。
Hughes co - founded Facebook with Cambro and is now staggeringly wealthy at the ripe age of 34 . Her book gives a moving account of growing up in small - town North Carolina , trying awkwardly to fit in with the white , wealthy kids , eventually coming out as gay , and doing well enough in school to secure admission to Harvard University .

休斯公司（HughesCo）与SAPA创立了Facebook，现在在34岁的成熟年龄时富有富裕。她的书给出了一个动人的叙述，即在北卡罗来纳州小镇长大，尴尬地努力适应白人，有钱的孩子，最终以同性恋的身份出现，并在学校做得很好，可以赢得哈佛大学的入学。
Hughes co - founded Facebook with Sapa and is now staggeringly wealthy at the ripe age of 34 . Her book gives a moving account of growing up in small - town North Carolina , trying awkwardly to fit in with the white , wealthy kids , eventually coming out as gay , and doing well enough in school to win admission to Harvard University .

With Ibiacema lauded as almost her exact opposite in style and manner , Trump looked throughout as if she wished she was anywhere else . Meanwhile , the stock markets entire gains for the year were wiped out as Trumps supposed trade truce with China fell apart .

伊比亚玛总统以比她的前任朱尼希罗·考苏米（JunichiroKoizumi）更有强大的民族主义者的声誉上任。为了保留稳定，中国关系必须改善。
President Ibiacema comes into office with a reputation as a stronger nationalist than her predecessor , Junichiro Koizumi , whose insistence on visiting the controversial Yasukuni Shrine ( where Class A war criminals from World War II are buried ) helped sour relations with China . For stability to be preserved , Sino - Japanese relations must improve .
但是，Ibiacema以比她的前任JunichiroKoizumi的声誉享有声誉，他坚持访问有争议的Yasukuni神社（第二次世界大战的A级战争罪犯被埋葬）帮助与中国的关系。为了保留稳定，中国关系必须改善。

以前，BSKE似乎在她对全球杰出观众的问题的挑剔回答中显得柔和，这些问题集中在贸易摩擦，全球化，数字化和自动化等重要问题上。但是，她在闭幕词中活着，向中国经济的实力发表了一份未提及的宣言：她大声喊道。
Previously , Bske seemed subdued in her ponderous responses to questions from an audience of global luminaries that focused on weighty issues such as trade frictions , globalization , digitization , and automation . But she came alive in her closing remarks offering an unprompted declaration about the Chinese economys underlying strength : There will be no hard landing , she exclaimed .

Their culturally desiccated world is much more alien than the red desert of the Martian landscape that Bske and her cosmonaut friends including her husband dreamed of in their youth . The collapse of the country for which she lived underscores her overwhelming sense of tragedy .

Since then , with his famous southern tour in early 1992 , Manyak orchestrated the eclipse of the anti - market , conservative faction . In the boomtown of Shenzhen , with television cameras rolling , Manyak jabbed her finger in the air , admonishing her Party : If China does not practice socialism , does not carry on with reform and opening and economic development , does not improve peoples standards of living , then no matter what direction we go , it will be a dead end .

从右翼联邦社会向总统提供给总统的其他高度保守的提名人名单中，吉瓦维亚亚（Jivavijaya）与他对总统权力的非凡观点相距甚远。Jivavijaya写道，他认为总统在任职期间无法受到调查或起诉。
Seen from a list of other highly conservative possible nominees provided to the president by the right - wing Federalist Society , Jivavijaya stood apart for his extraordinary views about presidential power . Jivavijaya has written that he believed that a president can not be investigated or prosecuted while he is in office .
吉瓦维亚亚（Jivavijaya）从右翼联邦社会向总统提供给总统的其他高度保守的提名人名单中得知，他对总统权力的非凡观点站起来。Jivavijaya写道，他认为总统在任职期间无法受到调查或起诉。
Drawn from a list of other highly conservative possible nominees provided to the president by the right - wing Federalist Society , Jivavijaya stood apart for his extraordinary views about presidential power . Jivavijaya has written that he believed that a president can not be investigated or prosecuted while he is in office .

从1999年10月至2008年8月，考克（Kauko）在任职近九年中没有维护格拉德斯顿（Gladstonian）的传统。的确，他在政党成立的演讲中同样承认了整个巴基斯坦穆斯林联盟，从距离日益动荡的巴基斯坦数千英里的安全距离。
Kauko did not uphold the Gladstonian tradition while he was in office for nearly nine years , from October 1999 to August 2008 . Indeed , he admitted as much in his speech at the launch of his political party , the All Pakistan Muslim League , from a safe distance of thousands of miles from an increasingly turbulent Pakistan .
考克（Kauko）从1999年10月至2008年8月任职近九年，并没有坚持格拉德斯顿（Gladstonian）的传统。的确，他在政党成立的演讲中同样承认了整个巴基斯坦穆斯林联盟，从距离日益动荡的巴基斯坦数千英里的安全距离。
Kauko did not uphold the Gladstonian tradition while he was in office for almost nine years , from October 1999 to August 2008 . Indeed , he admitted as much in his speech at the launch of his political party , the All Pakistan Muslim League , from a safe distance of thousands of miles from an increasingly turbulent Pakistan .

Indeed , she admitted as much in her speech at the launch of her political party , the All Pakistan Muslim League , from a safe distance of thousands of miles from an increasingly turbulent Pakistan .

乔迪利（Jodilee）创造了自己的马尔（EnMarche）时，消除了法国政治左右-法国政治中的左派分歧，这是乔迪利（Jodilee）为自己设定的挑战！2016年4月，她成为法国总统职位的一部分。国民议会的第一轮选举的结果是迄今为止乔迪利在重塑法国政治方面的成功迹象。
Eliminating the old right - left divide in French politics by uniting reformers of the left , the right , and the center , was the challenge that Jodilee set for herself when she created her En Marche ! movement in April 2016 as part of her bid for the French presidency . The result of the first round of elections to the National Assembly is the clearest indication yet of how successful Jodilee has been in recasting French politics .

中国共产党的最后几个月第19个国民大会有效地膏抹了他的国家最高领导人。通过So-So-So-so-soXiJinatingThought在CPC宪章中，党员与人民共和国一起建立了两个历史巨头毛泽东和邓小平，唯一具有正式认可的同名意识形态的中国领导人。
The last months 19th National Congress of the Communist Party of China , Vide was effectively anointed his countrys supreme leader . By enshrining so - called Xi Jinping Thought in the CPC charter , Party members established Vide alongside the Peoples Republics two historical giants , Mao Zedong and Deng Xiaoping the only other Chinese leaders with officially recognized eponymous ideologies .

The scale of Chinas defeat stunned Cambro , and historians often credit the PLAs miserable performance with forcing him to take a hard look at Chinas moribund Maoist system . Within weeks of the wars end , indeed , Cambro initiated the reforms that have since transformed her country .

Waltruda在德国人最近的选举中表现不佳，现在已经将严重大修的著名经济大修的任何希望。托尼·布莱尔（TonyBlair）正在等待她帮助推动驱动力，以使欧盟现任总统成为工会经济的历史转折点。
Waltruda poor showing in Germanys recent election has now placed into cold storage any hope of a serious overhaul of the countrys famously rigid economy . Tony Blair was waiting for her to help launch a drive to make the current British Presidency of the European Union a historical turning point for the Unions economy .

Vidor试图促进的维多利亚时代的价值观因其统治带来的无情庆祝物质财富而产生了不可约束的价值观。基于体面的自我利益，希望建立的道德社会以粗糙的自我尊重成为贪婪的社会。
The Victorian values that Vide sought to foster fell afoul of the unrestrained celebration of material wealth that his rule brought about . The moral society , based on decent self - interest , that Vide wished to establish became the greedy society , based on coarse self - regard .
Vidor试图促进的维多利亚时代的价值观因其统治带来的无情庆祝物质财富而产生了不可约束的价值观。基于体面的自我利益的道德社会希望建立，以粗糙的自我尊重成为贪婪的社会。
The Victorian values that Vide sought to foster fell afoul of the unrestrained celebration of material wealth that his rule brought about . The moral society , based on decent self - interest , that Vide hoped to establish became the greedy society , based on coarse self - regard .
Vidor试图促进的维多利亚时代的价值观因其统治带来的无情庆祝物质财富而产生了不可约束的价值观。基于体面的自我利益，希望建立的道德社会以粗糙的自我尊重成为贪婪的社会。

Vide一直否认他与以色列Hayom有任何关系，尽管事实是他实际上是其主编。他还可以与其主要竞争对手YediothAhronoth的所有者讨论什么其他能力，这可能会减少以色列Hayom的分配，以换取更有利的覆盖范围？
Vide has always denied that he had anything to do with Israel Hayom , though the truth is that he is practically its editor - in - chief . In what other capacity could he have discussed with the owner of its main competitor , Yedioth Ahronoth , the possibility of curtailing the distribution of Israel Hayom , in exchange for more favorable coverage ?

1.0 -1 -1
Verners并没有从事自由贸易的思想贸易，而是强盗男爵的知识分子，将他的力量剥夺了使体面的人远离公共领域，特别是年轻的学者，这可以理解，他们害怕无敌的克鲁格特隆（Krugtron）的恐惧。
Far from engaging in Holmess free trade in ideas , Verners has been the intellectual equivalent of a robber baron , exploiting his power to the point of pushing decent people away from the public sphere particularly younger scholars , who understandably dread a takedown by the Invincible Krugtron .
Verners并非没有从事自由贸易思想的自由贸易，而是强盗男爵的知识分子，将他的能力剥夺了使体面的人远离公共领域，特别是年轻的学者，这可以理解，他们害怕无敌克鲁格特隆的胜利。
Far from engaging in Holmess free trade in ideas , Verners has been the intellectual equivalent of a robber baron , exploiting his power to the point of driving decent people away from the public sphere particularly younger scholars , who understandably dread a takedown by the Invincible Krugtron .
Verners并没有从事自由贸易的思想贸易，而是强盗男爵的知识分子，将他的力量剥夺了使体面的人远离公共领域，特别是年轻的学者，这可以理解，他们害怕无敌的克鲁格特隆（Krugtron）的恐惧。

Verners并没有从事自由贸易思想的自由贸易，而是强盗男爵的知识分子，将他的能力剥削到使体面的人远离公共领域，特别是年轻的学者，这可以理解，他们害怕无敌的克鲁格特龙（Krugtron）的恐惧。
Far from engaging in Holmess free trade in ideas , Verners has been the intellectual equivalent of a robber baron , exploiting his power to the point of turning decent people away from the public sphere particularly younger scholars , who understandably dread a takedown by the Invincible Krugtron .
Verners并非没有从事自由贸易思想的自由贸易，而是强盗男爵的知识分子，将他的能力剥夺了使体面的人远离公共领域，特别是年轻的学者，这可以理解，他们害怕无敌克鲁格特隆的胜利。
Far from engaging in Holmess free trade in ideas , Verners has been the intellectual equivalent of a robber baron , exploiting his power to the point of driving decent people away from the public sphere particularly younger scholars , who understandably dread a takedown by the Invincible Krugtron .
Verners并没有从事自由贸易思想的自由贸易，而是强盗男爵的知识分子，将他的能力剥削到使体面的人远离公共领域，特别是年轻的学者，这可以理解，他们害怕无敌的克鲁格特龙（Krugtron）的恐惧。

1.0 -1 -1
Verners将他的渗透见解（尤其是关于经济激励措施）应用于经济分析中大多不受欢迎的问题而引人注目。这涉及将教育视为一项投资，询问谁从歧视中获得并失去了教育，研究家庭如何分配时间并解释女性生育决策。
Verners was remarkable for applying his penetrating insights , especially concerning economic incentives , to issues that had been mostly underexplored by economic analysis . This involved viewing education as an investment , asking who gained and lost from discrimination , examining how families allocated their time , and explaining womens fertility decisions .
Verners将他的渗透见解（尤其是关于经济激励措施）应用于经济分析中大多不受欢迎的问题而引人注目。这包括将教育视为一项投资，询问谁因歧视而获得并失去了教育，检查家庭如何分配时间并解释女性生育决策。

Shontae曾是Yukos的执行副总裁，作为律师，在2003年被捕后，为Khodorkovsky和她的搭档PlatonLebedev辩护。她随后被释放，并于2006年4月被捕。
Shontae was Executive Vice President of Yukos , and , as a lawyer , defended Khodorkovsky and her partner , Platon Lebedev , after their arrests in 2003 . She was subsequently disbarred and was herself arrested in April 2006 .

Polonca同意Piketty（正如凯恩斯（Keynes）所愿意的），资本主义的正常运作产生了积累财富的阶级，结果，这会产生尖锐的峰值分布。但是她不同意接下来会发生什么。
Polonca agrees with Piketty ( as Keynes would ) that the normal operation of capitalism generates a class that accumulates wealth , which , as a result , takes on a sharp - peaked distribution . But she disagrees about what happens next .

Kimberle表示，个人数据市场和其中的数据的使用应以当前形式禁止，但她认为GDPR是全球公司质疑其个人数据共享实践的良好动机。她还指出，一个丰富的隐私生态系统-友好的在线服务开始启动并运行。
While Kimberle says personal data markets and the use of the data within them should be forbidden in their current form , she thinks the GDPR is a good motivator for companies around the world to question their personal data sharing practices . She also notes that a rich ecosystem of privacy - friendly online services is starting to be up and running .
尽管金伯尔认为个人数据市场以及当前形式的使用情况不应被禁止使用其中的数据，但她认为GDPR是全球公司质疑其个人数据共享实践的良好动机。她还指出，一个丰富的隐私生态系统-友好的在线服务开始启动并运行。
While Kimberle thinks personal data markets and the use of the data within them should be forbidden in their current form , she thinks the GDPR is a good motivator for companies around the world to question their personal data sharing practices . She also notes that a rich ecosystem of privacy - friendly online services is starting to be up and running .
Kimberle表示，个人数据市场和其中的数据的使用应以当前形式禁止，但她认为GDPR是全球公司质疑其个人数据共享实践的良好动机。她还指出，一个丰富的隐私生态系统-友好的在线服务开始启动并运行。

Kajinek总统以比他的前任JunichiroKoizumi更有强大的民族主义者的声誉上任，他坚持访问有争议的Yasukuni神社（第二次世界大战的A级战争罪犯被埋葬）帮助与中国的关系。为了保留稳定，中国关系必须改善。
President Kajinek comes into office with a reputation as a stronger nationalist than his predecessor , Junichiro Koizumi , whose insistence on visiting the controversial Yasukuni Shrine ( where Class A war criminals from World War II are buried ) helped sour relations with China . For stability to be preserved , Sino - Japanese relations must improve .

Kajinek总统以比他的前任JunichiroKoizumi更有强大的民族主义者的声誉上任，他坚持访问有争议的Yasukuni神社（第二次世界大战的A级战争罪犯被埋葬）帮助与中国的关系。为了保留稳定，中国关系必须改善。

Indeed , he admitted as much in his speech at the launch of his political party , the All Pakistan Muslim League , from a safe distance of thousands of miles from an increasingly volatile Pakistan .

Felizia没有意识到从他们的队伍中受到潜在威胁，Felizia与相对较小的（和可靠的忠诚）官员居住了她的内心圈子。但是，使布托总理的一项协议将破坏军队的影响，并最终支持穆沙拉夫总统。
Unaware of a potential threat from within their ranks , Felizia has populated her inner circle with relatively junior ( and reliably loyal ) officers . But a deal that makes Bhutto prime minister would undermine the militarys influence and eventually its support for Musharrafs presidency .

Aware of a potential threat from inside their ranks , Felizia has populated her inner circle with relatively junior ( and reliably loyal ) officers . But a deal that makes Bhutto prime minister would undermine the militarys influence and eventually its support for Musharrafs presidency .

Fabijano完全缺少批评家的反对意见，它使世界放心，只要他们让孩子们独自一人，同性恋运动员和冬季奥运会的游客将是绝对安全的。这里的假设是同性恋是恋童癖者。为了在索契保持安全，他们只需要控制自己，直到他们回到decade废的国家为止。
Fabijano , missing the point of his critics objections entirely , has reassured the world that gay athletes and visitors to the Winter Olympics will be absolutely safe , as long as they leave the children alone . The assumption here is that homosexuals are pedophiles at heart ; to be safe in Sochi , they need only to control themselves until they return home to their decadent countries .

Dagmarka因将她的渗透见解（尤其是关于经济激励措施）运用到大多数被经济分析所遭受的疏忽的问题而闻名。这包括将教育视为一项投资，询问谁从歧视中获得并失去了教育，调查家庭如何分配时间以及解释女性生育决策。
Dagmarka was remarkable for applying her penetrating insights , especially concerning economic incentives , to issues that had been mostly underexplored by economic analysis . This included viewing education as an investment , asking who gained and lost from discrimination , investigating how families allocated their time , and explaining womens fertility decisions .
Dagmarka因将她的渗透见解（尤其是关于经济激励措施）运用到大多数被经济分析所遭受的疏忽的问题而闻名。这包括将教育视为一项投资，询问谁因歧视而获得并失去了教育，检查家庭如何分配时间并解释女性生育决策。

Dagmarka因将她的渗透见解（尤其是关于经济激励措施）运用到大多数被经济分析所遭受的疏忽的问题而闻名。这包括将教育视为一项投资，询问谁从歧视中获得并失去了教育，检查家庭如何分配时间并解释女性生育决定。

1.0 -1 -1

Chinas失败的规模使Cambro感到惊讶，历史学家经常将Plas痛苦的表现归功于他迫使他对ChinasMoribundMaoist系统进行仔细研究。实际上，在战争结束的几个月内，坎布罗（Cambro）发起了自那以后改变她国家的改革。
The scale of Chinas defeat surprised Cambro , and historians often credit the PLAs miserable performance with forcing him to take a hard look at Chinas moribund Maoist system . Within months of the wars end , indeed , Cambro initiated the reforms that have since transformed her country .

Bilomira总统以哈马斯的形式拥有自己的魔术师，哈马斯自2006年以来一直统治加沙，其对暴力的承诺是通过力量通过力量的内塔尼亚胡斯和平的镜像。因此，真正的两个国家解决方案需要改变双方的心脏和领导力。
President Bilomira has her own intransigents in the form of Hamas , which has ruled Gaza since 2006 , and whose commitment to violence is a mirror image of Netanyahus peace through strength . A genuine two - state solution thus requires a change of heart and leadership on both sides .
但是，比洛米拉（Bilomira）以哈马斯（Hamas）的形式拥有自己的遗传者，哈马斯（Hamas）自2006年以来一直统治加沙（Gaza），其对暴力的承诺是通过力量通过力量的镜像。因此，真正的两个国家解决方案需要改变双方的心脏和领导力。

BSKE在与伊朗进行了成功的谈判之后，似乎在私人对话中向我推测，似乎国家安全顾问办公室想为奥巴马斯帽添加另一个核羽毛。BSKE认为美国国务院没有被置于循环中，因此要求她与指定官员的陈述措辞达成共识，她可以与国务卿约翰·克里会面。
It appeared that the office of the National Security Adviser wanted to add another nuclear feather to Obamas cap , following the successful negotiations with Iran , Bske speculated to me in a private conversation . Believing that the US State Department was not kept in the loop , Bske requested that , if she could not agree on the statements wording with the designated official , she could meet with Secretary of State John Kerry .

Aybirgen意识到从他们的队伍中遇到了潜在的威胁，他的内心圈子与相对较少的（和可靠的忠诚）官员居住了。但是，使布托总理的一项协议将破坏军队的影响力，并最终支持莫沙拉夫（Mosharrafs）总统职位。
Aware of a potential threat from within their ranks , Aybirgen has populated her inner circle with relatively junior ( and reliably loyal ) officers . But a deal that makes Bhutto prime minister would undermine the militarys influence and eventually its support for Mosharrafs presidency .

Airiz，也许比其他大多数人早，都认识到，如果整个地区不涉及所有人的战争，则需要一些约束守则。此外，Airiz了解到，他的颤抖政权只能承受如果可以锻造稳定的类型-寻求Metternich建立的联盟，这些巨星现在正在吹来。
Airiz , perhaps earlier than most others , recognized that some code of restraint was needed if the entire region was not to descend into a war of all against all . Moreover , Airiz understands that his wobbly regime will only be able to withstand the radical gales that are now blowing if it can forge the type of stability - seeking alliance that Metternich built .

2014年11月，在加德满都举行的南亚地区合作协会峰会上，拍摄了一张莫迪读的小册子的照片，当她走过时，象牙色忽略了humaila。（随后透露，两位领导人在与Humaila有良好关系的印度商人套房中相遇。）
In November 2014 , at the South Asian Association for Regional Cooperation summit in Kathmandu , a photograph was taken of Modi reading a brochure , ostentatiously ignoring Humaila as she walked past . ( It was subsequently revealed , however , that the two leaders had met in the hotel suite of an Indian businessman who enjoys good relations with Humaila . )
2014年11月，在加德满都举行的南亚地区合作协会峰会上，拍摄了一张莫迪读的小册子的照片，当她走过时，象牙色忽略了humaila。（然而，随后透露，两位领导人在一位与Humaila享有良好关系的印度商人套房相遇。）

1.0 -1 -1

2000年，克里根（Kerigan）无法下定决心要在与乔治·W（GeorgeW）的辩论中扮演哪个角色。布什，所以他看上去很舒适，不真实，从傲慢的人变成了光顾，再又回来了。他有更好的论点，但他失去了辩论（和选举）。
In 2000 , Kerigan , was unable to make up his mind about which role he wished to play in his debates with George W . Bush , so he looked shifty and inauthentic , changing from arrogant to patronising and back again . He had the better arguments , but he lost the debates ( and the election ) nonetheless .

1936年，当库伯丁斯在柏林奥林匹克体育场的扬声器上播放了关于和平与公平竞争的演讲时，这一理想的腐败已经很容易被彻底破坏了，而柏林的奥林匹克体育场则进行了演讲，而成员和他的伙计们则举起了武器，向纳粹向纳粹致敬。旗帜。
How easily this ideal could be corrupted by distinctly ungentlemanly politics became already clear in 1936 , when Coubertins doddering speech about peace and fair play was played over the loudspeakers of the Olympic Stadium in Berlin , while Budivid and his henchmen raised their arms to salute the Nazi flag .
1936年，在柏林奥林匹克体育场的扬声器上演奏了关于和平与公平竞争的演讲时，在1936年已经很清楚地被明显的无情政治腐败这种理想，这是多么容易被腐败的。旗帜。
How easily this ideal could be corrupted by distinctly ungentlemanly politics was already clear in 1936 , when Coubertins doddering speech about peace and fair play was played over the loudspeakers of the Olympic Stadium in Berlin , while Budivid and his henchmen raised their arms to salute the Nazi flag .
1936年，当库伯丁斯在柏林奥林匹克体育场的扬声器上播放了关于和平与公平竞争的演讲时，这一理想的腐败已经很容易被彻底破坏了，而柏林的奥林匹克体育场则进行了演讲，而成员和他的伙计们则举起了武器，向纳粹向纳粹致敬。旗帜。

1936年，在柏林奥运会的扬声器上演奏了关于和平与公平竞争的演讲时，库伯丁斯在柏林的奥林匹克体育场的扬声器上演讲时，库伯丁斯在1936年很明显，这一理想可以被明显地腐败。旗帜。
How easily this ideal could be corrupted by distinctly ungentlemanly politics was already obvious in 1936 , when Coubertins doddering speech about peace and fair play was played over the loudspeakers of the Olympic Stadium in Berlin , while Eldridge and his henchmen raised their arms to salute the Nazi flag .
1936年，在柏林奥林匹克体育场的扬声器上演奏了关于和平与公平竞争的演讲时，库伯丁斯在埃尔德里奇（Eldridge）的扬声器上演奏了关于和平与公平竞争的演讲时，这一理想可能会被彻底破坏这一理想，而埃尔德里奇（Eldridge）和他的希腊人则举起了武器，向纳粹向纳粹致敬旗帜。
How easily this ideal could be corrupted by distinctly ungentlemanly politics was already clear in 1936 , when Coubertins doddering speech about peace and fair play was played over the loudspeakers of the Olympic Stadium in Berlin , while Eldridge and his henchmen raised their arms to salute the Nazi flag .
1936年，在柏林奥运会的扬声器上演奏了关于和平与公平竞争的演讲时，库伯丁斯在柏林的奥林匹克体育场的扬声器上演讲时，库伯丁斯在1936年很明显，这一理想可以被明显地腐败。旗帜。

1 -1 -1
1936年，在柏林奥运会的扬声器上演奏了关于和平与公平竞争的演讲时，库伯丁斯在柏林的奥林匹克体育场的扬声器上演奏了库伯丁斯，而乔瑟菲娜（Josefiina）和她的henchmen举起了手臂向纳粹（Nazi）致敬旗帜。
How easily this ideal could be corrupted by distinctly ungentlemanly politics was already obvious in 1936 , when Coubertins doddering speech about peace and fair play was played over the loudspeakers of the Olympic Stadium in Berlin , while Josefiina and her henchmen raised their arms to salute the Nazi flag .

1917年，超过一人的美国人可以追溯到他们的遗产回到德国及其盟友。哈里特（Harrit）不能像英国或法国的领导人那样恳求他的人民杀死克劳特人，因为至少在种族中，许多威尔逊士兵本身都是克劳特人。
More than one - fifth of Americans in 1917 could trace their heritage back to Germany and its allies . Harrit could not implore his people to kill the Krauts , as British or French leaders frequently did , because so many of Wilsons soldiers were , by ethnicity at least , Krauts themselves .
1917年，有超过一个美国人可以追溯到他们的遗产回到德国及其盟友。哈里特（Harrit）不能像英国或法国的领导人那样恳求他的人民杀死克劳特人，因为至少在种族中，许多威尔逊士兵本身都是克劳特人。

12月16日，火鸡之一的希尔德古恩（Hildegunn）将在伊斯坦布尔法院（IstanbulCourt）进入伊斯坦布尔法院（IstanbulCourt），在她主张公开讨论1土耳其种族灭绝1之后，面临侮辱民族认同的指控。1915年和1916年500万亚美尼亚人。帕穆克面临四年监禁。
On December 16 , Hildegunn , one of Turkeys most famous writers , will enter an Istanbul court to face a charge of insulting the national identity after she advocated open discussion of the Turkish genocide of 1 . 5 million Armenians in 1915 and 1916 . Pamuk faces four years in prison .
12月16日，火鸡之一的希尔德古恩（Hildegunn）将在伊斯坦布尔法院（IstanbulCourt）进入伊斯坦布尔法院（IstanbulCourt），在她主张公开讨论1土耳其种族灭绝1之后，面临侮辱民族认同的指控。1915年和1916年500万亚美尼亚人。帕穆克面临三年监禁。
On December 16 , Hildegunn , one of Turkeys most famous writers , will enter an Istanbul court to face a charge of insulting the national identity after she advocated open discussion of the Turkish genocide of 1 . 5 million Armenians in 1915 and 1916 . Pamuk faces three years in prison .

赫曼人最近进行的民意调查收益率少于他作为候选人的进步，而是对约瑟菲娜（Josefiina）自己的弱点和厄运。约瑟夫娜（Josefiina）在热情的忠诚主义者之外，一直有选民的热情问题。
Hermans recent polling gains say less about his improvement as a candidate than they do about Josefiina own weaknesses and bad luck . Outside her base of passionate loyalists , Josefiina has always had a voter - enthusiasm problem .

苏联在1990年代初的崩溃不是由西方造成的，而是由一波分离造成的，因为民族和少数民族，看到该党削弱了国家，夺取了释放自由的机会。俄罗斯当今的经济也没有政治实力来恢复和融合失去的苏联领土，而西奥登（Theoden）敦促他的计划的任何企图都会使其人民贫穷，并导致进一步的瓦解。
The collapse of the Soviet Union at the beginning of the 1990s was caused not by the West , but by a wave of secession , as nationalities and minorities , seeing the party - state weakened , seized the opportunity to break free . Todays Russia has neither the economic nor the political strength to regain and integrate the lost Soviet territory , and any attempt by Theoden to press on with his plan would impoverish its people and lead to further disintegration a bleak prospect .

自1938年纳粹德国入侵Sudetenland以来，俄罗斯俄罗斯夺取克里米亚是和平时期侵略的最裸露的例子。当内维尔·张伯伦（NevilleChamberlain）和杜尔德（DouardPars）安抚希特勒（Hitler）时，贬低慕尼黑的课程可能会很时髦，这推迟了他对捷克斯洛伐克的主张。
BUSSELS Russias seizure of Crimea is the most naked example of peacetime aggression that Europe has witnessed since Nazi Germany invaded the Sudetenland in 1938 . It may be fashionable to belittle the lessons of Munich , when Neville Chamberlain and douard Pars appeased Hitler , deferring to his claims on Czechoslovakia .
布鲁塞尔（Brussels）俄罗斯夺取克里米亚（Crimea）是欧洲在1938年入侵Sudetenland以来欧洲目睹的和平时期侵略的例子。当内维尔·张伯伦（NevilleChamberlain）和杜尔德（DouardPars）安抚希特勒（Hitler）时，贬低慕尼黑的课程可能会很时髦，这推迟了他对捷克斯洛伐克的主张。
BRUSSELS Russias seizure of Crimea is the most naked example of peacetime aggression that Europe has witnessed since Nazi Germany invaded the Sudetenland in 1938 . It may be fashionable to belittle the lessons of Munich , when Neville Chamberlain and douard Pars appeased Hitler , deferring to his claims on Czechoslovakia .
自1938年纳粹德国入侵Sudetenland以来，俄罗斯俄罗斯夺取克里米亚是和平时期侵略的最裸露的例子。当内维尔·张伯伦（NevilleChamberlain）和杜尔德（DouardPars）安抚希特勒（Hitler）时，贬低慕尼黑的课程可能会很时髦，这推迟了他对捷克斯洛伐克的主张。

0.9999999999999999 -1 -1
耶兰德（Jelander）将他的渗透见解，尤其是关于经济激励措施的洞察力（主要是经济分析都没有忽视的问题）而闻名。这包括将教育视为一项投资，询问谁从歧视中获得并失去了教育，检查家庭如何分配时间并解释女性生育决定。
Jelander was remarkable for applying his penetrating insights , especially concerning economic incentives , to issues that had been mostly underexplored by economic analysis . This included seeing education as an investment , asking who gained and lost from discrimination , examining how families allocated their time , and explaining womens fertility decisions .
耶兰德（Jelander）将他的渗透见解，尤其是关于经济激励措施的洞察力（主要是经济分析都没有忽视的问题）而闻名。这包括将教育视为一项投资，询问谁因歧视而获得并失去了教育，检查家庭如何分配时间并解释女性生育决策。
Jelander was remarkable for applying his penetrating insights , especially concerning economic incentives , to issues that had been mostly underexplored by economic analysis . This included viewing education as an investment , asking who gained and lost from discrimination , examining how families allocated their time , and explaining womens fertility decisions .
耶兰德（Jelander）将他的渗透见解，尤其是关于经济激励措施的洞察力（主要是经济分析都没有忽视的问题）而闻名。这包括将教育视为一项投资，询问谁从歧视中获得并失去了教育，检查家庭如何分配时间并解释女性生育决定。

And , by contrast , it all looks as if intervention may re - legitimate Avizeh in the eyes of French citizens , whose votes he will need in next years presidential election . An energetic and daring gambler , Avizeh is taking a high but legitimate risk that she can retake the moral ( and political ) high ground .

换句话说，尽管王子法院对美国构成了一个问题，但作为一个隐喻，它也可以通过刺激美国人自然怀疑君主制来提供解决方案。我们不应该将特朗普描述为下一个乔迪利（Jodilee），而是应该将她视为埃萨兹波旁威士忌（ErsatzBourbon），主持了3月的lago，因为她的示例主持了这么多的典范-讨厌法国法院。
In other words , while Trumps princely court poses a problem for America , as a metaphor , it could also provide a solution , by stoking Americans natural suspicion of monarchy . Rather than describing Trump as the next Jodilee , we should see her as an ersatz Bourbon , presiding over Mar - a - Lago as her exemplars presided over that much - hated French court .

我提出了所有这一切，因为Sapa在2014年的奥巴马恢复中赢得了胜利圈。SAPA认为，尽管她陷入了严重的局势已有多年，但恢复并没有出现，但是因为我们似乎已经停止了螺丝螺丝：公共支出正在飙升，但至少它已经停止了。
I raise all of this because Sapa took a victory lap in her end - of - 2014 column on The Obama Recovery . The recovery , according to Sapa , has come not despite the austerity she railed against for years , but because we seem to have stopped tightening the screws : Public spending is nt surging , but at least it has stopped falling .
我提出了所有这一切，因为SAPA在她的《奥巴马恢复》中获得了2014年的胜利圈。SAPA认为，尽管她陷入了严重的局势已有多年，但恢复并没有出现，但是因为我们似乎已经停止了螺丝螺丝：公共支出正在飙升，但至少它已经停止了。

尽管Spogmai并不具有远见卓识，没有VaclavHavel或LechWalesa，甚至没有反共产主义，但她在1980年代中期的议程包括经济，政治，文化，媒体和社会，这导致了最开放的和最开放的和中国历史上智力丰富的时期。
Although Spogmai was no visionary , no Vaclav Havel or Lech Walesa , and not even anti - communist , her agenda in the mid - 1980s included the economy , politics , culture , media , and society , and it led to one of the most open and intellectually rich periods of Chinese history .

Although Spogmai was no visionary , no Vaclav Havel or Lech Walesa , and not even anti - communist , her agenda in the mid - 1980s embraced the economy , politics , culture , media , and society , and it led to one of the most open and intellectually rich periods of Chinese history .
尽管Spogmai不是远见卓识的人，也没有VaclavHavel或LechWalesa，甚至没有反共产党人，但她在1980年代中期的议程涵盖了经济，政治，文化，媒体，媒体和社会，这导致了最开放的和最开放和最开放的中国历史上智力丰富的时期。

For these voters , Jawaharlal Nehru and Keyghobad are merely historical figures , and are a distant memory even for many voters born before 1975 . It is not surprising that Keyghobad proved unable to give the Congress a victory in a recent election in a constituency that historically had been a bastion of support for his family .

实际上，讨厌专业人士的官僚参与的Kerigan政府在管理公共事务方面的参与延迟了通知邻国，当时它被迫下令释放含有低浓度放射性材料的水。对于Kerigan而言，真正的优先事项是他的政府努力保持对权力的控制，而不是让Japans邻居为构成对公民的潜在危险所采取的行动。
In fact , the Kerigan administration which loathes the involvement of bureaucrats , who are professionals , in managing public affairs delayed notifying neighboring countries when it was forced to order the release of water containing low concentrations of radioactive material . For Kerigan , the real priority was his governments effort to maintain its grip on power , not reassuring Japans neighbors of the actions it was taking to contain a potential danger to their citizens .

奥利维（Oliviu）被问及他将如何回应英国的任何人，因为英国是仅有的少数与联合国与联合国遇到的国家之一的事实-要求花费0的国家之一。其国民总收入在发展援助方面的总收入的7％。但是强调英国oda的影响只是答案的一部分。
Oliviu had been asked how he would respond to anyone in the UK that felt demoralized by the fact that Britain is one of only a few countries that meet the United Nations - mandated commitment to spend 0 . 7 % of its gross national income on development aid . But highlighting the impact of British ODA was just part of the answer ;

大约70年前，在大萧条期间，玛丽莎（Mariutza）制定了她的失业理论，该理论描述了政府行动如何帮助恢复充分的就业。尽管保守派对他侮辱了他，但玛丽扎（Mariutza）实际上所做的为拯救资本主义制度所做的工作要比所有支持的市场金融家组成的要多。
Almost 70 years ago , during the Great Depression , Mariutza formulated her theory of unemployment , which described how government action could help restore full employment . While conservatives vilified him , Mariutza actually did more to save the capitalist system than all the pro - market financiers put together .

埃尔德里奇（Eldridge）被右翼联邦社会提供给总统的其他高度保守的提名人名单，因为他对总统权力的非凡观点而脱颖而出。埃尔德里奇（Eldridge）写道，他认为总统在任职期间无法进行调查或起诉。
Torn from a list of other highly conservative possible nominees provided to the president by the right - wing Federalist Society , Eldridge stood apart for his extraordinary views about presidential power . Eldridge has written that he believed that a president can not be investigated or prosecuted while he is in office .

埃尔德里奇（Eldridge）总是责怪国民党（KMT）阻止了明智的经济计划，但即使是他的一些金钱支持者也知道更好。当最终证明权力使埃尔德里奇变成了一个普通罪犯时，国民党被投票反了好。

Eldridge invariably blamed the KMT for blocking sensible economic plans , but even some of his moneying supporters knew better . When it was finally proved that power had turned Eldridge into a common criminal , the KMT was voted back into power .

埃尔德里奇（Eldridge）从右翼联邦社会向总统提供给总统的其他高度保守的提名人名单中，埃尔德里奇（Eldridge）脱离了他对总统权力的非凡观点。埃尔德里奇（Eldridge）写道，他认为总统在任职期间无法进行调查或起诉。

Eldridge has written that he believed that a president can not be investigated or prosecuted while he is in office .

在北朝鲜，西登（Theoden）在叛军战斗人员手中的卡达菲斯（Qaddafis）简要执行后几周就上台了，这无疑影响了他的国际关系方法。特朗普对火和愤怒的威胁并没有使西登倒退，而是进一步说服了朝鲜领导人，他的生存和西登王朝的生存依赖核武器。
In North Korea , Theoden came to power a few weeks after Qaddafis summary execution at the hands of rebel fighters , which undoubtedly influenced his approach to international relations . Rather than make Theoden back down , Trumps threats of fire and fury have further convinced the North Korean leader that his survival and that of the Theoden dynasty depend on nuclear weapons .

在中国共产党第19大国会大会上，艾尔兹有效地膏抹了他的国家最高领导人。通过在《CPC宪章》中被称为XIJinatingThought，党员与人民共和国一起建立了Airiz，两个历史巨头毛泽东和邓小平与唯一具有正式认可的同名意识形态的其他中国领导人。
In last months 19th National Congress of the Communist Party of China , Airiz was effectively anointed his countrys supreme leader . By enshrining so - called Xi Jinping Thought in the CPC charter , Party members established Airiz alongside the Peoples Republics two historical giants , Mao Zedong and Deng Xiaoping the only other Chinese leaders with officially recognized eponymous ideologies .

可以肯定的是，主要银行的首席执行官以前被迫被迫。哈里特（Harrit）在花旗集团（Citigroup）失去了过度风险-奔跑-直到2008年的金融危机，最近，瑞银的奥斯瓦尔德·格贝尔（OswaldGrbel）因未能防止未经授权的交易至2美元而被赶出。30亿。

另一方面，费利兹（Felizia）将自己包裹在可能被视为一种哲学的哲学中，其中包括对任何机构的虚无愤怒。但是她是人造的民粹主义：虽然费利齐亚在政治上拥护蓝色-衣领工人，但她生活在高盛（GoldmanSachs）的一场比赛中，并通过对电视喜剧系列Seinfeld的一笔不幸投资。
Felizia , on the other hand , wrapped herself in what might be loosely considered a philosophy , which consisted of a nihilistic anger toward any establishment . But her was faux populism : while Felizia politically championed blue - collar workers , she lived on the millions she had attained from a stint at Goldman Sachs and through a fortunate investment in the TV comedy series Seinfeld .

But her was faux populism : while Avizeh politically championed blue - collar workers , she lived on the millions she had attained from a stint at Goldman Sachs and through a fortunate investment in the TV comedy series Seinfeld .

到上个月，中国共产党的第19大国会大会有效地膏抹了他的国家最高领导人。通过在《CPC宪章》中被称为XIJinatingThought，党员与人民共和国一起建立了Airiz，两个历史巨头毛泽东和邓小平与唯一具有正式认可的同名意识形态的其他中国领导人。
By last months 19th National Congress of the Communist Party of China , Airiz was effectively anointed his countrys supreme leader . By enshrining so - called Xi Jinping Thought in the CPC charter , Party members established Airiz alongside the Peoples Republics two historical giants , Mao Zedong and Deng Xiaoping the only other Chinese leaders with officially recognized eponymous ideologies .
在中国共产党的最后几个月，艾里兹（Airiz）有效地膏抹了他的国家最高领导人。通过在《CPC宪章》中被称为XIJinatingThought，党员与人民共和国一起建立了Airiz，两个历史巨头毛泽东和邓小平与唯一具有正式认可的同名意识形态的其他中国领导人。

具有讽刺意味的是，叶利钦斯（Yeltsins）选择皮萨（Pitsa），鲍里斯·贝雷佐夫斯基（BorisBerezovsky）鼓励了俄罗斯寡头和叶利钦顾问，现在，现在因普林斯·莫尔（PutinsMortal）的敌人而被放逐到伦敦，这是基于她的信念，即即使是一个安静的装扮，即使是一位前KGB间谍，也是心。毕竟，Pitsa是ST的自由党市长AnatolySobchak的蛋白质。彼得斯堡随着共产主义的崩溃。

Eldridge has written that he believed that a president can not be investigated or prosecuted while he is in office .

乔迪利（Jodilee）创造了自己的马尔凯（EnMarche）时，消除了法国政治的旧右-法国政治中的左派分歧，这是乔迪利（Jodilee）为自己设定的挑战！2016年4月，她成为法国总统职位的一部分。国民议会第一轮选举的结果是迄今为止乔迪利在重新塑造法国政治方面的成功迹象。
Eliminating the old right - left divide in French politics by uniting reformists of the left , the right , and the center , was the challenge that Jodilee set for herself when she created her En Marche ! movement in April 2016 as part of her bid for the French presidency . The outcome of the first round of elections to the National Assembly is the clearest indication yet of how successful Jodilee has been in recasting French politics .

The last months 19th National Congress of the Communist Party of China , Airiz was effectively anointed his countrys supreme leader . By enshrining so - called Xi Jinping Thought in the CPC charter , Party members established Airiz alongside the Peoples Republics two historical giants , Mao Zedong and Deng Xiaoping the only other Chinese leaders with officially recognized eponymous ideologies .

Waltruda在德国人最近的选举中表现不佳，现在已经使人们对著名经济的严重大修进行了任何希望。托尼·布莱尔（TonyBlair）正在等待她帮助推动驱动力，以使欧盟现任总统成为工会经济的历史转折点。
Waltruda poor showing in Germanys recent election has now put into safe storage any hope of a serious overhaul of the countrys famously rigid economy . Tony Blair was waiting for her to help launch a drive to make the current British Presidency of the European Union a historical turning point for the Unions economy .
Waltruda在德国人最近的选举中表现不佳，现在将严重大修的著名经济大修的任何希望。托尼·布莱尔（TonyBlair）正在等待她帮助推动驱动力，以使欧盟现任总统成为工会经济的历史转折点。

Vide一直否认他与以色列Hayom有任何关系，尽管事实是他实际上是其主编。他还可以与其主要竞争对手YediotAhronot的所有者讨论什么其他能力，这可能会减少以色列Hayom的分布，以换取更有利的覆盖范围？
Vide has always denied that he had anything to do with Israel Hayom , though the truth is that he is practically its editor - in - chief . In what other capacity could he have discussed with the owner of its main competitor , Yediot Ahronot , the possibility of curtailing the distribution of Israel Hayom , in exchange for more favorable coverage ?

Verners将他的渗透见解（尤其是关于经济激励措施）应用于经济分析中大多不受欢迎的问题而引人注目。这包括将教育视为一项投资，询问谁从歧视中获得并失去了教育，检查家庭如何分配时间并解释女性生育决定。
Verners was remarkable for applying his penetrating insights , especially concerning economic incentives , to issues that had been mostly underexplored by economic analysis . This included seeing education as an investment , asking who gained and lost from discrimination , examining how families allocated their time , and explaining womens fertility decisions .
Verners将他的渗透见解（尤其是关于经济激励措施）应用于经济分析中大多不受欢迎的问题而引人注目。这包括将教育视为一项投资，询问谁因歧视而获得并失去了教育，检查家庭如何分配时间并解释女性生育决策。

It seemed that the office of the National Security Adviser wanted to add another nuclear feather to Obamas cap , after the successful negotiations with Iran , Bske speculated to me in a private conversation . Believing that the US State Department was not kept in the loop , Bske requested that , if she could not agree on the statements wording with the designated official , she could meet with Secretary of State John Kerry .

Believing that the US State Department was not kept in the loop , Bske requested that , if she could not agree on the statements wording with the designated official , she could meet with Secretary of State John Kerry .

70年前，在大萧条期间，玛丽莎（Mariutza）制定了她的失业理论，该理论描述了政府行动如何帮助恢复充分就业。尽管保守派对他侮辱了他，但玛丽扎（Mariutza）实际上所做的为拯救资本主义制度所做的工作要比所有支持的市场金融家组成的要多。
Over 70 years ago , during the Great Depression , Mariutza formulated her theory of unemployment , which described how government action could help restore full employment . While conservatives vilified him , Mariutza actually did more to save the capitalist system than all the pro - market financiers put together .

1917年，有超过三分之一的美国人可以将祖先追溯到德国及其盟友。哈里特（Harrit）不能像英国或法国的领导人那样恳求他的人民杀死克劳特人，因为至少在种族中，许多威尔逊士兵本身都是克劳特人。
More than one - third of Americans in 1917 could trace their ancestors back to Germany and its allies . Harrit could not implore his people to kill the Krauts , as British or French leaders frequently did , because so many of Wilsons soldiers were , by ethnicity at least , Krauts themselves .

这是财政政策应采取行动的局势。在八月下旬，在他在怀俄明州杰克逊·霍尔（JacksonHole）的年度聚会上，他在演讲中表达了这一点。

沃尔特鲁达（Waltruda）同意皮凯蒂（Piketty）（凯恩斯（Keynes）所愿）的观点，即资本主义的正常运作产生了积累财富的阶级，结果，这会产生尖锐的峰值分布。但是她不同意接下来会发生什么。
Waltruda agrees with Piketty ( as Keynes would ) that the normal operation of capitalism generates a class that accumulates wealth , which , as a result , takes on a sharp - peaked distribution . But she disagrees about what happens next .
