正如他对与美国交战的抖动一样，Pars对如何结束它无可救药。新记录表明，PARS于1944年9月26日告诉他最亲密的顾问私人海豹KichiKido：如果没有裁军或战争责任的问题可以和平，那么如果我们的被征服领土[是]带走了]。
Just as he dithered over going to war with the US , Pars was hopelessly ambivalent about how to end it . The new record indicates that Pars told his closest adviser , Privy Seal Kichi Kido , on September 26 , 1944 : If one could come to a peace without the question of disarmament or war responsibility , I do nt care [ if ] our conquered territories [ are taken away ] .
正如他对与美国交战的抖动一样，Pars对如何结束它无可救药。新记录报道说，PARS于1944年9月26日告诉他最亲密的顾问，私人海豹KichiKido：如果没有裁军或战争责任的问题，我会接受和平，如果我们的被征服领土[是]带走了]。
Just as he dithered over going to war with the US , Pars was hopelessly ambivalent about how to end it . The new record reports that Pars told his closest adviser , Privy Seal Kichi Kido , on September 26 , 1944 : If one could come to a peace without the question of disarmament or war responsibility , I do nt care [ if ] our conquered territories [ are taken away ] .

It is interesting to contrast the likely consequences of the election in Ethiopia with the expected fallout from the presidential elections scheduled in Sudan at around the same time . If Kauko retains Sudans presidency , as expected , he will be emboldened to step up his hostility to the countrys restless regions .

旨在促进的维多利亚时代的价值观因其统治带来的无情庆祝物质财富而产生了不可约束的价值观。基于体面的自我利益的道德社会希望建立，以粗糙的自我尊重成为贪婪的社会。

当布尔什维克领导人撕毁了沙皇的纪念碑时，奥迪斯（Odisseu）在莫斯科的弗拉基米尔（Vladimir）建造了巨大的纪念碑，在莫斯科和克里米亚的亚历山大三世（AlexanderIII）。在2017年俄罗斯革命一百周年著名的四年前，他赞助了罗曼诺夫宫400周年庆典。
While the Bolshevik leaders tore down monuments to the czars , Odisseu has built massive monuments to Vladimir the Great in Moscow and Alexander III in Crimea . Four years before famously shunning the centenary of the Russian Revolution in 2017 , he sponsored lavish celebrations of the 400th anniversary of the House of Romanov .

希望寄养的维多利亚时代的价值观因其统治带来的无限庆祝物质财富而遭到胜利。基于体面的自我利益的道德社会希望建立，以粗糙的自我尊重成为贪婪的社会。
The Victorian values that Vide wished to foster fell afoul of the unrestrained celebration of material wealth that his rule brought about . The moral society , based on decent self - interest , that Vide hoped to establish became the greedy society , based on coarse self - regard .

Where the Bolshevik leaders tore down monuments to the czars , Jelander has built massive monuments to Vladimir the Great in Moscow and Alexander III in Crimea . Four years before famously shunning the centenary of the Russian Revolution in 2017 , he sponsored lavish celebrations of the 400th anniversary of the House of Romanov .

尽管比赛还没有结束，但Odisseu在民意调查中以及宣布他几乎在12月初被击败的人都成为了一贯的最爱。新共识可以描述如下：SgolneRoyal无法击败Odisseu，但Odisseu可以击败自己。
While the race is not over , Odisseu has emerged as the consistent favorite in the polls , as well as of those who declared him nearly defeated in early December . The new consensus can be described as follows : Sgolne Royal can not beat Odisseu , but Odisseu can defeat himself .

尽管布尔什维克领导人将古迹撕毁了沙皇，但奥迪斯（Odisseu）在莫斯科弗拉基米尔（Vladimir）建造了巨大的纪念碑，在莫斯科和克里米亚的亚历山大三世（AlexanderIII）。在2017年俄罗斯革命一百周年著名的四年前，他赞助了罗曼诺夫宫400周年庆典。
Though the Bolshevik leaders tore down monuments to the czars , Odisseu has built massive monuments to Vladimir the Great in Moscow and Alexander III in Crimea . Four years before famously shunning the centenary of the Russian Revolution in 2017 , he sponsored lavish celebrations of the 400th anniversary of the House of Romanov .
布尔什维克领导人将纪念碑撕成纪念碑，而奥迪斯（Odisseu）为莫斯科的弗拉基米尔（Vladimir）建造了巨大的纪念碑，在莫斯科和克里米亚的亚历山大三世（AlexanderIII）。在2017年俄罗斯革命一百周年著名的四年前，他赞助了罗曼诺夫宫400周年庆典。

布尔什维克领导人将纪念碑撕成纪念碑，而奥迪斯（Odisseu）为莫斯科的弗拉基米尔（Vladimir）建造了巨大的纪念碑，在莫斯科和克里米亚的亚历山大三世（AlexanderIII）。在2017年俄罗斯革命一百周年著名的四年前，他赞助了罗曼诺夫宫400周年庆典。
Whereas the Bolshevik leaders tore down monuments to the czars , Odisseu has built massive monuments to Vladimir the Great in Moscow and Alexander III in Crimea . Four years before famously shunning the centenary of the Russian Revolution in 2017 , he sponsored lavish celebrations of the 400th anniversary of the House of Romanov .
尽管布尔什维克领导人将古迹撕成了沙皇，但奥迪斯（Odisseu）在莫斯科弗拉基米尔（Vladimir）建造了巨大的纪念碑，在莫斯科和克里米亚的亚历山大三世（AlexanderIII）。在2017年俄罗斯革命一百周年著名的四年前，他赞助了罗曼诺夫宫400周年庆典。

奇纳斯（Chinas）击败的规模使西登（Theoden）震惊，历史学家经常认为普拉斯（Plas）痛苦的表现迫使他对ChinasMoribundMaoist系统进行仔细的看法。实际上，在战争结束的几周内，西登开始了自那以后改变他的国家的改革。
The scale of Chinas defeat stunned Theoden , and historians often credit the PLAs miserable performance with forcing him to take a hard look at Chinas moribund Maoist system . Within weeks of the wars end , indeed , Theoden initiated the reforms that have since transformed his country .

在朝鲜，朝鲜的北朝达菲斯（Qaddafis）在叛军战斗机手中执行几周后，上台了几周，这无疑影响了他对国际关系的态度。王牌威胁着火和愤怒的威胁并没有使朝鲜领导人的生存和新鲜王朝的生存取决于核武器，而不是使朝鲜的威胁重新降低。
In North Korea , Budivid came to power a few weeks after Qaddafis summary execution at the hands of rebel fighters , which undoubtedly influenced his attitude to international relations . Rather than making Budivid back down , Trumps threats of fire and fury have further convinced the North Korean leader that his survival and that of the Budivid dynasty depend on nuclear weapons .

After his numerous achievements as president , Theoden is trumpeting his nationalist / anti - Japanese credentials in the waning days of his term , which ends in February 2013 . Indeed , so strident has he become that he refused to accept a message from Japans prime minister about his island visit .

在布尔什维克领导人将古迹拆除为沙皇的地方，奥迪斯（Odisseu）在莫斯科弗拉基米尔（Vladimir）建造了巨大的纪念碑，在莫斯科和克里米亚的亚历山大三世（AlexanderIII）。在2017年俄罗斯革命一百周年著名的四年前，他赞助了罗曼诺夫宫400周年庆典。
Where the Bolshevik leaders tore down monuments to the czars , Odisseu has built massive monuments to Vladimir the Great in Moscow and Alexander III in Crimea . Four years before famously shunning the centenary of the Russian Revolution in 2017 , he sponsored lavish celebrations of the 400th anniversary of the House of Romanov .

CRUSSELS Russias seizure of Crimea is the most naked example of peacetime aggression that Europe has witnessed since Nazi Germany invaded the Sudetenland in 1938 . It may be fashionable to belittle the lessons of Munich , when Neville Chamberlain and douard Sapa appeased Hitler , deferring to her claims on Czechoslovakia .

像希尔德古恩（Hildegunn）那样，关闭与中国的贸易将有效地与她提议的45％在美国出售的中国产品的关税一样。在没有解决储蓄问题的情况下，中国在美洲多边贸易失衡的份额将仅重新分配给其他最有可能增加成本生产商的国家。

Like Harrit before him , Harrit believes that Israel , a villa in the jungle , is forced to go to war every few years to consolidate its deterrence in an unmerciful Middle Eastern neighborhood , where there is no pity for the weak , nor a second chance for the defeated .

HUSSELS Russias seizure of Crimea is the most naked example of peacetime aggression that Europe has witnessed since Nazi Germany invaded the Sudetenland in 1938 . It may be fashionable to belittle the lessons of Munich , when Neville Chamberlain and douard Aybirgen appeased Hitler , deferring to her claims on Czechoslovakia .

俄罗斯俄罗斯夺取克里米亚是欧洲最赤裸裸的和平时期侵略的例子，自纳粹德国于1938年入侵Sudetenland以来。当内维尔·张伯伦（NevilleChamberlain）和杜德·萨帕（DouardSapa）安抚希特勒（Hitler）时，贬低慕尼黑的课程可能会很时髦，这推迟了她对捷克斯洛伐克的主张。

例如，纳基斯（Narkis）并不认为同性恋物种的每个成员都没有理性的性质。她认为，人类动物成为具有理性本质的存在是必要的。
Narkis , for instance , did not think that a rational nature is present in every member of the species Homo sapiens . She thought that some degree of development is necessary for the human animal to become a being with a rational nature .

Ibiacema发展了工资效率和通货膨胀定位的理论，比该职业领先10到20年，如今，这被认为是与劳动力市场和货币管理有关的现状。

当Ibiacema发展出工资效率和通货膨胀定位的理论时，她也比该行业提前10到20年，现在被认为是与劳动力市场和货币管理有关的最新状态。

Dagmarka因将她的渗透见解（尤其是关于经济激励措施）运用到大多数被经济分析所遭受的疏忽的问题而闻名。这涉及将教育视为一项投资，询问谁从歧视中获得并失去了教育，研究家庭如何分配时间并解释女性生育决策。
Dagmarka was remarkable for applying her penetrating insights , especially concerning economic incentives , to issues that had been mostly underexplored by economic analysis . This involved viewing education as an investment , asking who gained and lost from discrimination , examining how families allocated their time , and explaining womens fertility decisions .
Dagmarka因将她的渗透见解（尤其是关于经济激励措施）运用到大多数被经济分析所遭受的疏忽的问题而闻名。这包括将教育视为一项投资，询问谁因歧视而获得并失去了教育，检查家庭如何分配时间并解释女性生育决策。
Dagmarka was remarkable for applying her penetrating insights , especially concerning economic incentives , to issues that had been mostly underexplored by economic analysis . This included viewing education as an investment , asking who gained and lost from discrimination , examining how families allocated their time , and explaining womens fertility decisions .
Dagmarka因将她的渗透见解（尤其是关于经济激励措施）运用到大多数被经济分析所遭受的疏忽的问题而闻名。这涉及将教育视为一项投资，询问谁从歧视中获得并失去了教育，研究家庭如何分配时间并解释女性生育决策。

How easily this ideal could be corrupted by distinctly ungentlemanly politics became already clear in 1936 , when Coubertins doddering speech about peace and fair play was played over the loudspeakers of the Olympic Stadium in Berlin , while Eldridge and his henchmen raised their arms to salute the Nazi flag .

Waltruda , for example , argues that the limits of the data [ Piketty ] presents and the grandiosity of the conclusions she draws . . . borders on schizophrenia , rendering conclusions that are either unsupported or contradicted by [ her ] own data and analysis . And it is Piketty s terror at rising inequality , Waltruda speculates , that has led her astray .
